{"department_text": "Home & Outdoors", "level": 1, "url": "http://www.newegg.com/Home-Outdoors/Store?name=Home-Outdoors", "text": "Home & Outdoors", "department_url": "http://www.newegg.com/Home-Outdoors/Store?name=Home-Outdoors", "description_title": "Newegg's Home & Office Store News", "keyword_count": {"home": 3, "newegg": 2, "office": 5}, "description_wc": 315, "description_text": "Products: Coffee technology made easy Rather than making an entire pot of coffee for a few people, single cup brewers provide the simple convenience the world sometimes lacks. While technology continues to grow at a breakneck pace, coffee drinkers will be happy to know certain technology is not rocket science-related. The Keurig line of coffee brewers is perfect for using in the home or in a large office. Everyone has different taste, and the single K-cups provide different flavors without the need to constantly brew large quantities of coffee. Some of the features offered by Keurig include different brew sizes, including 4 oz, 6 oz, 8 oz, 10 oz and 12 oz varieties. The removable drip tray allows travel mugs to be filled, while the iced beverage setting provides great drinks on those hot days. People drink coffee and lots of it. Many cannot start the day without a cup, and the Keurig line of coffee brewers provides the best of both worlds: quantity and quality. Although people have their routines, the K-cup offers something different in a world that is constantly changing. Whether you're looking for home appliances, kitchen cookware, or office supplies, Newegg carries a wide variety of items for your shopping pleasure. We carry all manner of office furniture, including office chairs of all types for every level of employee or guest. Even kitchen appliances are included. Whether you're seeking small kitchen appliances, or home kitchen appliances, or cookware, we have a huge selection for your review. We even carry personal care items and the latest in Newegg gear, so you can represent your favorite shopping site. From bbq grills to office chairs, we carry it all! WARNING: The products listed on this page and in this category may contain chemicals known to the State of California to cause cancer, or birth defects or other reproductive harm.", "keyword_density": {"home": "1.0", "newegg": "0.6", "office": "1.6"}, "department_id": 8},
