{"department_text": "Software", "level": 1, "url": "http://www.newegg.com/Software/Store", "text": "Software", "department_url": "http://www.newegg.com/Software/Store", "description_title": "Software", "keyword_count": {"software": 10}, "description_wc": 191, "description_text": "Newegg is the clear choice for all your software needs. We stock a wide array of boxed & downloadable software , as well as software license packs for business use. We've got you covered if you're looking for productivity software like Microsoft Office, or programming software titles like Visual Studio or SQL Server. We offer digital media titles, such as AutoCAD or the Adobe Creative Suite that includes DreamWeaver, Photoshop, Illustrator, Fireworks and more. Make sure your computer is secure with internet security & antivirus software . Get the latest operating system -- OS X for Macs, or Windows 8, Windows XP or Windows 7 for the PC. Keep track of your finances with accounting titles like Intuit's TurboTax or Quicken. All these titles are just the tip of the iceberg. Newegg also sells software books and manuals, educational and reference software, home improvement , games , server software and more. Find all this and more in Newegg's Software Store! WARNING: The products listed on this page and in this category may contain chemicals known to the State of California to cause cancer, or birth defects or other reproductive harm.", "keyword_density": {"software": "5.3"}, "department_id": 5},
