{"department_text": "Gaming", "level": 1, "url": "http://www.newegg.com/Gaming/Store", "text": "Gaming", "department_url": "http://www.newegg.com/Gaming/Store", "description_title": "Newegg Gaming", "keyword_count": {"gaming": 2, "newegg": 2}, "description_wc": 209, "description_text": "Newegg's video games store is as diverse as the games themselves. Get your daily dose of PC games , check out a console system like the PS4 , Xbox One , or Nintendo Wii U , or take your hobby on the road with a Nintendo 3DS or PS Vista . We sell all the hottest video game consoles including the PS4 and Xbox One , and offer a variety of bundled combos to choose from. Portable systems like the Nintendo 3DS come in multiple colors, and both the Xbox 360 and PS3 offer packages that include extra controllers or games . Speaking of games, we have thousands of titles available, whether you're looking for PS4 games , Xbox One games , PS3 games , Xbox 360 games , Wii U games , PS Vista games or 3DS games. PC gaming addicts also have a vast selection of PC games and Mac games to choose from, as well as accessories such as game controllers , joysticks, and racing wheels. Expand your horizons in Newegg's gaming store! WARNING: The products listed on this page and in this category may contain chemicals known to the State of California to cause cancer, or birth defects or other reproductive harm.", "keyword_density": {"gaming": "1.0", "newegg": "1.0"}, "department_id": 6},
{"department_text": "Cell Phones & Cell Phone Accessories", "level": 1, "url": "http://www.newegg.com/Cell-Phones-Cell-Phone-Accessories/Store/ID-140", "text": "Cell Phones & Cell Phone Accessories", "department_url": "http://www.newegg.com/Cell-Phones-Cell-Phone-Accessories/Store/ID-140", "description_title": "Cell Phones", "keyword_count": {"cell phones": 2, "phones": 9}, "description_wc": 385, "description_text": "Modern technology has made it easier to stay connected. Smartphones have a functionality that is more in-line with most computers than with older cell phones. Almost everyone has a phone with them at all times now, but it can be difficult to figure out which device would be best to purchase. Some shoppers may be turned off by all the extra bells and whistles a smartphone has, but there are still plenty of plain old cell phones available. These devices, now sometimes referred to as \"feature phones,\" can make calls and send texts but have only a few other functions, so users can stay in contact without being distracted by apps and games. By contrast, the market is flooded with different smartphones for consumers who want to buy the most modern gadget available. A varied selection of devices is available, the specifics of which largely depend on which carrier you choose. If the phone you want is not available from your network provider, consider looking at unlocked devices, which are not restricted to any one carrier's frequency. With all the extra features included in smartphones, you may want to buy accessories to make sure your device is reaching its potential. For example, music-streaming subscribers may want to find a pair of Bluetooth-capable headphones so they can listen to all their favorite songs without being wired to their phone. Smartphones are somewhat fragile because of their slim builds and large screens, so a case is necessary to protect the device. There are hard shells and soft body-gloves designed specifically for every make and model. iPhone 5 cases and covers are available, along with enclosures for many other popular models, and are ideal for shoppers who want their new phone to stay in top shape and be protected even if accidentally dropped. Heavier users may require extra chargers, because their phone's battery is unlikely to last through the entire day. Most smartphones can charge via an USB cord, which is perfect for office workers who want to make sure their device will be alive during the commute home. Shoppers can find any phone and accessory to suit their needs. Users should take the time to decide what their expectations are from a device, so they can make a more informed purchase.", "keyword_density": {"cell phones": "1.0", "phones": "2.3"}, "department_id": 7},
{"department_text": "Electronics", "level": 1, "url": "http://www.newegg.com/Electronics/Store", "text": "Electronics", "department_url": "http://www.newegg.com/Electronics/Store", "description_title": "Electronics", "keyword_count": {"electronics": 5}, "description_wc": 206, "description_text": "Newegg's electronics selection, from LCD TVs to GPS navigation to MP3 players , is beyond compare. Get your home entertainment center started with a widescreen high definition 1080p LCD or plasma HDTV from Samsung or LG . Continue on to our home audio store to browse speakers, MP3 players , stereo receivers and amplifiers from top-end manufacturers like Bose and Polk Audio . Now that your home theater system is on its way, move on to the accessories! Our electronics store is the doorway to exciting categories such as digital photo frames , electronic gadgets , projectors , home video , home audio , and headphones . Working from home can be a breeze with products from our office equipment and telephones & VOIP . We can even help you get on the road with car electronics , GPS navigation & accessories , MP3 players , portable electronics , hand tools and power tools , and two way radios . Take a look and you'll agree, Newegg is the best place to shop for electronics! WARNING: The products listed on this page and in this category may contain chemicals known to the State of California to cause cancer, or birth defects or other reproductive harm.", "keyword_density": {"electronics": "2.6"}, "department_id": 4},
{"department_text": "Computer Hardware", "level": 0, "url": "http://www.newegg.com/Video-Cards-Video-Devices/Category/ID-38", "text": "Video Cards & Video Devices", "department_url": "http://www.newegg.com/Computer-Hardware/Store", "description_title": "Video Cards", "parent_url": "http://www.newegg.com/Computer-Hardware/Store", "keyword_count": {"video cards": 2, "video": 11}, "description_wc": 235, "description_text": "Use this link for more information on Video Cards in our Learning Center Want to play the latest, most advanced PC games or watch true high definition (HDTV) videos? Newegg.com always provides the hottest video card products from the manufacturers you trust: ASUS, EVGA, GIGABYTE, HIS, MSI, Palit, PNY, Sapphire, XFX, and others. Now you can even double the graphics performance of your computer with NVIDIA SLI technology or ATI Crossfire technology for a gaming experience that is second to none! Understanding Video Card Specifications The video card processes all graphics-related work (especially 3D) and delivers the resultant output to a connected display/monitor. Video card improvements move along at breakneck speeds - a new generation of video cards often replaces the old within 3-6 months. The GPU (Graphics Processing Unit) basically determines the features (e.g. DirectX 9 or DirectX10/OpenGL, HDR, and SLI or CrossFire) and performance level of a video card. Besides the GPU, the video memory specs (including video memory type, size and clock speed), interface (AGP or PCI Express), and I/O ports are should all be taken into account before purchasing a video card. WARNING: Products with exposed solder may contain lead, a chemical known to the State of California to cause cancer, birth defects and other reproductive harm. Please wash hands after handling internal components and motherboards and avoid inhalation of fumes if heating the solder.", "parent_text": "Computer Hardware", "keyword_density": {"video cards": "1.7", "video": "4.7"}, "department_id": 1},
