{"department_text": "Gaming", "nr_products": 46, "level": -1, "url": "http://www.newegg.com/Xbox-Accessories/SubCategory/ID-243", "text": "Xbox Accessories", "department_url": "http://www.newegg.com/Gaming/Store", "description_title": "X-Box Accessories", "parent_url": "http://www.newegg.com/Video-Game-Console-Accessories/Category/ID-276", "keyword_count": {"box": 7, "x": 16, "box accessories": 4}, "description_wc": 179, "description_text": "As you might expect from a video game system made by Microsoft, Xbox is loaded with high-tech gaming options. In fact, purchasing an Xbox before you buy a DVD player, CD player, and MP3 player can save you hundreds of dollars. To fully unlock the awesome potential of this system, however, you need to purchase Xbox accessories. We've Got Great Xbox Accessories Here at Newegg There are numerous game controllers that are more appropriate for certain games than the standard controller. For example, you can purchase a steering wheel/pedal combination controller for auto racing games. You will also find wireless controllers, pressure-sensitive controllers, and many other specialty game pads in our online catalog. Other popular Xbox accessories available here at Newegg include networking equipment, game organizers, and remote controls. An Xbox is capable of so much more than the video game consoles of yesteryear. If you are looking to uncover the potential your system has, look no further than this website. We have plenty of Xbox accessories sold at the best prices on the Internet.", "parent_text": "Video Game Console Accessories", "keyword_density": {"box": "3.9", "x": "8.9", "box accessories": "4.5"}, "department_id": 6},
