{"department_text": "Gaming", "nr_products": 989, "level": -1, "url": "http://www.newegg.com/PS3-Accessories/SubCategory/ID-547", "text": "PS3 Accessories", "department_url": "http://www.newegg.com/Gaming/Store", "description_title": "PS3 Accessories", "parent_url": "http://www.newegg.com/Video-Game-Console-Accessories/Category/ID-276", "keyword_count": {"ps3": 4, "ps3 accessories": 1, "accessories": 2}, "description_wc": 304, "description_text": "The PlayStation 3 is a multimedia hub that's well-suited to a wide range of users, even those who don't have an extensive video game collection. With streaming services, a built-in Blu-ray player and internet connectivity, there are plenty of ways you can stay entertained with Sony's console. Picking out the right PS3 accessories can create an even better experience while using the device, by enhancing all of its best features. A controller is a basic necessity for every user. Consoles typically only come with one, so having extra controllers is necessary if you want to invite friends to play a game. You can pick and choose from numerous colors. Don't forget to buy a charger, as well. PS3s sync with new controllers via the wired connection, and without it, once a battery dies it's dead for good. For people that use video services but have a hard time searching for movies and TV shows with the on-screen keyboard, there are external keyboards available. You won't have to navigate to different letters with the analog sticks after buying a mini-keyboard that syncs with your PS3. As the Blu-ray player was a major part of the PS3's appeal for many, a remote control may be more intuitive to use than controllers and make on-screen navigation much simpler. Additionally, movies will look even better with a HDMI cable for a higher resolution picture. For gamers who like to play online, a headset may be the perfect accessory to enhance the experience. You can use this tool to strategize with teammates or psych out an opponent during a heated basketball or football game. Buying the right PlayStation 3 accessories can make the console even more fun to use and enhance all your favorite features.", "parent_text": "Video Game Console Accessories", "keyword_density": {"ps3": "1.3", "ps3 accessories": "0.7", "accessories": "0.7"}, "department_id": 6},
{"nr_products": 2770, "level": -1, "url": "http://www.newegg.com/PSP-Accessories/SubCategory/ID-502", "text": "PSP Accessories", "department_url": "http://www.newegg.com/Gaming/Store", "description_wc": 0, "parent_url": "http://www.newegg.com/Video-Game-Console-Accessories/Category/ID-276", "parent_text": "Video Game Console Accessories", "department_text": "Gaming", "department_id": 6},
{"department_text": "Gaming", "nr_products": 1035, "level": -1, "url": "http://www.newegg.com/Nintendo-Wii-Accessories/SubCategory/ID-546", "text": "Nintendo Wii Accessories", "department_url": "http://www.newegg.com/Gaming/Store", "description_title": "Wii Accessories", "parent_url": "http://www.newegg.com/Video-Game-Console-Accessories/Category/ID-276", "keyword_count": {"wii accessories": 3, "wii": 8}, "description_wc": 298, "description_text": "The Wii is an amazing, family-friendly console with a variety of motion-sensor-dependent games. By tipping the Wii-mote one way or another, changing the internal gyroscope's orientation, you can partake in a variety of games in a much more immersive way than previous systems could provide. However, some of these movements may feel disjointed and unnatural without the help of certain Wii accessories. Sports games especially benefit from these peripherals. Attachments give the controller a much more realistic feel, so you won't have to suffer a ponderous pantomime when you're trying to golf or play tennis, two of the most popular activities on the console. There are also extra add-ons for bowling, archery and other sports to enhance your gaming experience. Steering wheels are essential for racing games and come in a variety of colors to match your controller. Of course, having a controller in the first place is essential, and the Wii only comes with one white Wii-mote and Nunchuck. The colors and shapes available for the system are much broader than that one option, however. You can mix and match colors and finishes, or even switch out wristbands to totally personalize the look and feel. At the end of the day, don't forget to buy a charging station as well and the right rechargeable batteries, so you can keep getting the best performance from your Wii accessories. Be sure to also buy the right kind of cables as part of your Wii accessories purchase. Some games have high-definition content that you can't fully enjoy without the right composite cables and other attachments. Extension cords and enhanced sensor bars for Wii-mote connectivity can also maximize your gaming experience, giving your console and remotes more reach.", "parent_text": "Video Game Console Accessories", "keyword_density": {"wii accessories": "2.0", "wii": "2.7"}, "department_id": 6},
