{"department_text": "Gaming", "nr_products": 88, "level": -1, "url": "http://www.newegg.com/Nintendo-DS-Accessories/SubCategory/ID-244", "text": "Nintendo DS Accessories", "department_url": "http://www.newegg.com/Gaming/Store", "description_title": "Nintendo DS Accessories", "parent_url": "http://www.newegg.com/Video-Game-Console-Accessories/Category/ID-276", "keyword_count": {"nintendo ds": 6, "nintendo ds accessories": 3, "accessories": 5, "ds": 10}, "description_wc": 169, "description_text": "Nintendo DS revolutionizes handheld gameplay. With two ultra bright screens, 3D graphics, touch-screen technology and wireless communication, you can challenge yourself or your friends anywhere, anytime. It's lightweight and compact for portability, and there are hundreds of complex and engaging games available. Nintendo DS Accessories Add Convenience While Nintendo DS is simple to transport, it's still inconvenient to carry it in your hands all day. Some Nintendo DS accessories make it possible to carry your system without holding it in your hands or stashing it in a bag. If you're taking your Nintendo DS on a trip, you'll want an easy way to transport it together with your games, accessories, and batteries. Here at Newegg, we sell various Nintendo DS accessories that will make life a little easier and maximize your enjoyment of this great video game system. With the widest selection of accessories at the best prices, we can help you make your gaming experience even better, on the road or at home.", "parent_text": "Video Game Console Accessories", "keyword_density": {"nintendo ds": "7.1", "nintendo ds accessories": "5.3", "accessories": "3.0", "ds": "5.9"}, "department_id": 6},
{"nr_products": 167, "level": -1, "url": "http://www.newegg.com/Product/ProductList.aspx?Submit=ENE&N=100006946%204016&IsNodeId=1&name=Televisions", "text": "Televisions", "department_url": "http://www.newegg.com/Electronics/Store", "description_wc": 0, "parent_url": "http://www.newegg.com/Store/RecertifiedStore.aspx?RecertifiedStoreID=32&name=Refurbished-Electronics", "parent_text": "Refurbished Electronics", "department_text": "Electronics", "department_id": 4},
{"department_text": "Gaming", "nr_products": 1467, "level": -1, "url": "http://www.newegg.com/General-Game-Console-Accessories/SubCategory/ID-247", "text": "General Game Console Accessories", "department_url": "http://www.newegg.com/Gaming/Store", "description_title": "Video Game Console Accessories", "parent_url": "http://www.newegg.com/Video-Game-Console-Accessories/Category/ID-276", "keyword_count": {"video game console": 3, "video game console accessories": 2, "video game": 4, "video": 6, "accessories": 3}, "description_wc": 161, "description_text": "Today's video game systems are capable of things we never thought were possible a decade ago. However, not all gaming options are possible without the right video game console accessories. There are numerous accessories available right here at Newegg, such as headsets, specialty controllers, and many others. Video Game Console Accessories in Our Online Catalog Modern video game consoles aren't just computers but are entertainment hubs that can be attached to your home theater and home network for internet access. Surround sound effects, high-quality music and live internet gaming further enhances the total gaming experience. To make life easier when it comes to switching inputs, changing connections and so on we do offer a selection of Audio Video selectors. With the ability to handled HD signals over HDMI connections you can fully take advantage of surround sounds, HD audio and HD video like never before. See our full selection to find the right setup for your gaming needs.", "parent_text": "Video Game Console Accessories", "keyword_density": {"video game console": "5.6", "video game console accessories": "5.0", "video game": "5.0", "video": "3.7", "accessories": "1.9"}, "department_id": 6},
{"department_text": "Gaming", "nr_products": 42, "level": -1, "url": "http://www.newegg.com/Gamecube-Accessories/SubCategory/ID-245", "text": "Gamecube Accessories", "department_url": "http://www.newegg.com/Gaming/Store", "description_title": "Game Cube Accessories", "parent_url": "http://www.newegg.com/Video-Game-Console-Accessories/Category/ID-276", "keyword_count": {"game": 15, "cube": 8, "accessories": 6, "game cube accessories": 1, "cube accessories": 3}, "description_wc": 291, "description_text": "GameCube accessories can serve several different purposes--organizing your collection, improving gaming capabilities, and enhancing your enjoyment of the system. Whether you want to take on your opponents online or you need to pack up your system and take it with you, we have the accessories you need for a one-of-a-kind gaming experience. Game Cube Accessories Add to the Fun! A GameCube system operates like a computer. It has memory, a central processing unit, and accepts commands from external controllers in the same way your computer accepts commands from a keyboard and mouse. Like a computer, there are several accessories you can purchase for a GameCube. One of the most commonly purchased accessories is an additional controller. Additional controllers make it possible for multiple people to play at the same time. You may also want a wireless controller that lets you play from anywhere in the room. There are also specialty game pads, such as a racer wheel, that are designed to enhance specific games. You can also purchase memory cards for your GameCube. These cards plug into the GameCube and save vital gaming information, such as which levels players have reached, the transactions conducted in sports games, special characters, and current scores. If you're a frequent gamer, you may be interested in a memory card with up to 64 MB of memory. Modern video game systems, like GameCube, are capable of so much more than the Nintendo and Sega of yesteryear. Here at Newegg, we offer numerous GameCube accessories that help maximize your enjoyment of the latest video game technology. Best of all, our prices cannot be beat. You can purchase the same games you might find elsewhere and still have money left in your wallet.", "parent_text": "Video Game Console Accessories", "keyword_density": {"game": "5.2", "cube": "2.7", "accessories": "2.1", "game cube accessories": "1.0", "cube accessories": "2.1"}, "department_id": 6},
