{"department_text": "Automotive", "nr_products": 3023, "level": -1, "url": "http://www.newegg.com/Car-Subwoofers/SubCategory/ID-708", "text": "Car Subwoofers", "department_url": "http://www.newegg.com/Store/Promotion.aspx?storeid=19&name=Auto", "description_title": "Car Subwoofers", "parent_url": "http://www.newegg.com/Car-Electronics/Category/ID-283?name=Car-Electronics", "keyword_count": {"car": 7, "car subwoofers": 5}, "description_wc": 262, "description_text": "To get the best out of your car audio system and really rock the block, car subwoofers are the way to go. Whether you're looking to totally overhaul your interior and turn it into a performance machine or if you'd just prefer a boost in quality music enjoyment while on the go, car subwoofers will enhance your audio experience. To make your windows rattle, car subwoofers enhance bass quality by amplifying and feeding the audio signal back through an enclosure between 8 and 21 inches in diameter to produce a frequency of 20 to 200 Hz. The lower the frequency, the higher quality the sound will be - and the bigger the beats. The subwoofer will also filter out other frequencies, allowing for better quality and producing a clearer sound. Depending on the quality of your hardware and the inputs you provide it with, you can establish a crossover point where the treble and bass are perfectly balanced, providing the ultimate mix of highs and lows for playback enjoyment. For more balanced output, car subwoofers can give you the ability to fine-tune your listening experience in infinitely more satisfying ways than a standard car audio system right off the factory line can provide. Choosing your own hardware and getting a custom installation can give you the performance and quality you may only otherwise experience at the theater. Combining compact and affordable audio options that are on the level of high-end versions with sophisticated output adjustments, car subwoofers allow you to adjust your audio levels to optimize the listening experience.", "parent_text": "Car Electronics", "keyword_density": {"car": "2.7", "car subwoofers": "3.8"}, "department_id": 10},
