{"department_text": "Automotive", "nr_products": 35925, "level": -1, "url": "http://www.newegg.com/All-Bluetooth-Headsets-Accessories/SubCategory/ID-565", "text": "All Bluetooth Headsets & Accessories", "department_url": "http://www.newegg.com/Store/Promotion.aspx?storeid=19&name=Auto", "description_title": "Bluetooth Headsets", "parent_url": "http://www.newegg.com/Car-Electronics/Category/ID-283?name=Car-Electronics", "keyword_count": {"bluetooth headsets": 4, "bluetooth": 5}, "description_wc": 273, "description_text": "Hands-free devices are great and can be useful in many situations - not just when you're in the car. With a number of sleek styles and variable options, Bluetooth headsets can integrate with phones, computers, music devices and more to increase ease of use and keep your hands free for more important things. Mono Bluetooth headsets clip over one ear and are useful for walking around in public or taking a call in the car where there are plenty of other things that require your attention. Keeping one ear open will alert you to other conversations or potential situations in your immediate area that require a response and Bluetooth headsets let you do just that without taking away the use of one of your hands. Also, seeing as many U.S. states have laws restricting phone use - including texting and phone calls - while driving, Bluetooth headsets will keep you in touch with friends and co-workers without the risk of getting a ticket or putting other motorists in danger. A stereo Bluetooth headset covers both ears and is useful for playing video games or listening to music. You can go out for a walk or to the gym with your iPod or MP3 player, and not worry about getting a headphone cord tangled on yourself or the workout equipment. You'll be able to get up from your computer and get a drink without taking off your headphones or missing out on a minute of in-game or online chatter. You can even sync it to your game consoles and use it to wirelessly talk to friends on your PS3, XBox or Wii.", "parent_text": "Car Electronics", "keyword_density": {"bluetooth headsets": "2.9", "bluetooth": "1.8"}, "department_id": 10},
