{"department_text": "Ultrabooks & Tablets", "nr_products": 1950, "level": -1, "url": "http://www.newegg.com/Mice/SubCategory/ID-65", "text": "Mice", "department_url": "http://www.newegg.com/Ultrabooks-Tablets/Store/ID-125", "description_title": "Wireless Mice, Optical Mice, Laser Mice and Trackball Mice", "parent_url": "http://www.newegg.com/Laptop-Accessories/Category/ID-26?name=Ultrabook-Accessories", "keyword_count": {"wireless": 4, "mice": 3}, "description_wc": 113, "description_text": "Use this link for more information on Computer Mice in our Learning Center At Newegg you can choose from a massive selection of computer mice from industry leading manufacturers including wired and wireless products, as well as sleek space-saving designs for notebook computers and ergonomic mice for the utmost in user comfort and gaming performance regardless of hand-orientation. Brands featured at Newegg include Microsoft, Kensington, Logitech, Targus and others in configurations of RF wireless, Fast RF wireless, Bluetooth Wireless, and standard PS/2 and USB wired interfaces. With a mouse to fit every computer performance need Newegg has what you need. For more information, please see our Computer Mouse Buying Guide.", "parent_text": "Ultrabook Accessories", "keyword_density": {"wireless": "3.5", "mice": "2.7"}, "department_id": 2},
