{"department_text": "Ultrabooks & Tablets", "nr_products": 309, "level": -2, "url": "http://www.newegg.com/All-Laptop-Hard-Drives/SubCategory/ID-380", "text": "All Laptop Hard Drives", "department_url": "http://www.newegg.com/Ultrabooks-Tablets/Store/ID-125", "description_title": "Laptop / Notebook Hard Drives", "parent_url": "http://www.newegg.com/Laptop-Accessories/Category/ID-26?name=Ultrabook-Accessories", "keyword_count": {"laptop notebook hard drives": 1, "hard drives": 2, "laptop": 2, "hard": 4, "drives": 4, "notebook hard": 2, "notebook": 4}, "description_wc": 135, "description_text": "Use this link for more information on Laptop / Notebook Hard Drives in our Learning Center Looking for a replacement notebook hard drive or simply not satisfied with the performance of the original hard drive in your notebook computer? Newegg.com offers a large selection of notebook/laptop hard drives with storage capacities perfectly tailored to your requirements, as well as products that can contribute to higher levels of system performance for maximum enjoyment from your movies, pictures and games. Select from manufacturers such as Hitachi, Fujitsu, Seagate, Toshiba, Western Digital and Samsung with capacity limits ranging from 40GB to 320GB. Additionally, while most drives are SATA 1.5Gb/s we also carry a fair share of ATA-6 and SATA 3.0Gb/s drives too. Speed are in standard formats of 4200 RPM, 5400 RPM, and 7200 RPM.", "parent_text": "Ultrabook Accessories", "keyword_density": {"laptop notebook hard drives": "3.0", "hard drives": "3.0", "laptop": "1.5", "hard": "3.0", "drives": "3.0", "notebook hard": "3.0", "notebook": "3.0"}, "department_id": 2},
{"department_text": "Ultrabooks & Tablets", "nr_products": 4989, "level": -2, "url": "http://www.newegg.com/Laptop-Cases-Bags/SubCategory/ID-482", "text": "Laptop Cases & Bags", "department_url": "http://www.newegg.com/Ultrabooks-Tablets/Store/ID-125", "description_title": "Laptop Cases and Bags", "parent_url": "http://www.newegg.com/Laptop-Accessories/Category/ID-26?name=Ultrabook-Accessories", "keyword_count": {"laptop": 9, "laptop cases": 4}, "description_wc": 273, "description_text": "Laptop cases are essential for students and professionals who need to be able to take their work everywhere. Because of the fragile nature of laptop PCs, a regular bag or backpack just won\u2019t cut it - you need to protect your valuable documents and media. Not only do laptop cases protect the exterior in the event of a bump or fall, but they offer added cushioning that ensures the sensitive interior hardware stays intact as well. At Newegg you\u2019ll find affordable, stylish options perfect for any professional. Need a way to tote your work while still looking sharp? Consider a laptop briefcase or over-the-shoulder messenger case. Our professional models are both rugged and stylish. Most include several lockable zipper compartments to store your office supplies, and feature ergonomic handles and/or and adjustable shoulder straps for maximum versatility. Those who travel frequently can find models that feature trolley straps, to ensure the case stays in place when stored on top of a rolling suitcase. Students may be more interested in a backpack laptop case, which are suitable for larger laptops and offer ample storage space for textbooks, notebooks and other supplies. Backpack laptop cases are easy to carry around campus, and many models offer lifetime warranties, so you know they\u2019ll be able to keep up with your busy lifestyle. If you don\u2019t travel much and need something a little simpler, consider a notebook sleeve. These items offer all the protection you need without the frills. A laptop is more than just a computer - it\u2019s an investment. Protect yours with one of our many specially designed laptop cases.", "parent_text": "Ultrabook Accessories", "keyword_density": {"laptop": "3.3", "laptop cases": "2.9"}, "department_id": 2},
