e bundled with instructional DVDs and manuals that guide amateurs through the installation process step-by-step so they don't accidentally damage their system. Upgrading to a solid state drive from a hard drive can make any computer more efficient and convenient to use.", "parent_text": "Ultrabook Accessories", "keyword_density": {"solid state": "1.3", "drives": "2.3", "solid state drives": "1.0"}, "department_id": 2},
{"department_text": "Ultrabooks & Tablets", "nr_products": 1018760, "level": -1, "url": "http://www.newegg.com/Laptop-Batteries-AC-Adapters/SubCategory/ID-538", "text": "Laptop Batteries / AC Adapters", "department_url": "http://www.newegg.com/Ultrabooks-Tablets/Store/ID-125", "description_title": "Laptop Batteries & Chargers", "parent_url": "http://www.newegg.com/Laptop-Accessories/Category/ID-26?name=Ultrabook-Accessories", "keyword_count": {"chargers": 1, "laptop": 8, "batteries": 4, "laptop batteries": 1}, "description_wc": 310, "description_text": "There aren't many devices that can compete with the computing power and mobility that laptops offer. You can take notebooks anywhere as long as the battery is fully charged or there's an electrical outlet available to serve as a power source. Unfortunately, laptop batteries degrade over time - they store less electricity and die faster as they age. Even the best power supplies start to wear down after months of consistent use. For laptops that have a removable battery, it's easy find a replacement unit. If you know the make and model of your laptop, you can find the right battery easily. Because computers have different connection ports, it's important to find the power supply built specifically for your line of laptop. Some manufacturers offer universal batteries for notebooks that they no longer produce or support. A functioning AC adapter is another necessity for every computer, as no battery can last more than a few hours on a single charge. Like the batteries, it's important to find a compatible laptop charger for a notebook's electrical jack. Some users bring their laptops everywhere - from home to work or school and everywhere in between. Chargers can wear out from being repeatedly unplugged, and if they break there's no way to keep the notebooks they are connected to from losing power. Having a backup on hand in case of emergencies eliminates any unnecessary stress caused by waiting for a replacement. For added convenience, use one as a travel charger and leave the other at home, so you don't have to constantly unplug an adapter every time you go out. Until computer companies invent and produce everlasting batteries, it's important to have the necessary electrical equipment for a laptop. Without the right battery or charger, no computer will be functional after a single day of use.", "parent_text": "Ultrabook Accessories", "keyword_density": {"chargers": "0.3", "laptop": "2.6", "batteries": "1.3", "laptop batteries": "0.6"}, "department_id": 2},
{"department_text": "Ultrabooks & Tablets", "nr_products": 466, "level": -2, "url": "http://www.newegg.com/Business-Projectors/SubCategory/ID-42", "text": "Business Projectors", "department_url": "http://www.newegg.com/Ultrabooks-Tablets/Store/ID-125", "description_title": "Business Projectors", "parent_url": "http://www.newegg.com/Projectors/Category/ID-343", "keyword_count": {"business": 2, "projectors": 5, "business projectors": 1}, "description_wc": 119, "description_text": "Use this link for more on Business Projectors in our Learning Center Newegg.com offers a rich selection of projectors using LCD or DLP and from mainstream to professional.We carry projectors from Epson, InFocus, Mitsubishi, Sony, NEC and others. These days, projectors come in a wide range of resolutions and luminosities, for small offices or large lecture halls! Home and business users alike will be able to find projectors that fit and function perfectly both for the office and the home and enjoy maximum visual quality and impact as well as enhanced work efficiency. WARNING: The products listed on this page may contain chemicals known to the State of California to cause cancer, or birth defects or other reproductive harm.", "parent_text": "Projectors", "keyword_density": {"business projectors": "1.7", "projectors": "4.2", "business": "1.7"}, "department_id": 2},
