{"department_text": "Ultrabooks & Tablets", "nr_products": 309, "level": -1, "url": "http://www.newegg.com/All-Laptop-Hard-Drives/SubCategory/ID-380", "text": "All Laptop Hard Drives", "department_url": "http://www.newegg.com/Ultrabooks-Tablets/Store/ID-125", "description_title": "Laptop / Notebook Hard Drives", "parent_url": "http://www.newegg.com/Laptop-Accessories/Category/ID-26?name=Ultrabook-Accessories", "keyword_count": {"laptop notebook hard drives": 1, "hard drives": 2, "laptop": 2, "hard": 4, "drives": 4, "notebook hard": 2, "notebook": 4}, "description_wc": 135, "description_text": "Use this link for more information on Laptop / Notebook Hard Drives in our Learning Center Looking for a replacement notebook hard drive or simply not satisfied with the performance of the original hard drive in your notebook computer? Newegg.com offers a large selection of notebook/laptop hard drives with storage capacities perfectly tailored to your requirements, as well as products that can contribute to higher levels of system performance for maximum enjoyment from your movies, pictures and games. Select from manufacturers such as Hitachi, Fujitsu, Seagate, Toshiba, Western Digital and Samsung with capacity limits ranging from 40GB to 320GB. Additionally, while most drives are SATA 1.5Gb/s we also carry a fair share of ATA-6 and SATA 3.0Gb/s drives too. Speed are in standard formats of 4200 RPM, 5400 RPM, and 7200 RPM.", "parent_text": "Ultrabook Accessories", "keyword_density": {"laptop notebook hard drives": "3.0", "hard drives": "3.0", "laptop": "1.5", "hard": "3.0", "drives": "3.0", "notebook hard": "3.0", "notebook": "3.0"}, "department_id": 2},
