{"department_text": "PCs & Laptops", "level": 0, "url": "http://www.newegg.com/All-in-One-PCs/Category/ID-355", "text": "All-in-One PCs", "department_url": "http://www.newegg.com/PCs-Laptops/Store", "description_title": "All-in-One PCs", "parent_url": "http://www.newegg.com/PCs-Laptops/Store", "keyword_count": {"pcs": 10, "one": 10, "one pcs": 9}, "description_wc": 186, "description_text": "Use this link for more on All-in-One PCs in our Learning Center Looking for a powerful, ready-to-use All-in-One PCs for the home or office? All-in-One PCs here refers to a completely pre-built PC and Monitor together, including an integrated webcam and Wi-Fi connectivity. Most importantly, All-in-One PCs is easier to setup than a traditional Desktop PCs. All-in-One PCs are offered by brand name manufacturers, like ASUS, Hewlett-Packard, Acer, DELL, Lenovo, Gateway and Sony VAIO or SIs (Systems Integrators) and are typically offered with full system warranties. All-in-One PCs comes with big screens, loads of power and memory to get things done. Stylish space-saving designs make All-in-One PCs a great PC to your home or office. Besides that, most new All-in-One PCs have plenty of memory and storage for big projects in business. Its vivid and stunning displays and great processing power for rich multimedia and intense gaming. Moreover, many All-in-One PCs are touch-enabled with large tilting screens for hands-on interaction.", "parent_text": "PCs & Laptops", "keyword_density": {"pcs": "5.4", "one pcs": "9.7", "one": "5.4"}, "department_id": 3},
