{"department_text": "PCs & Laptops", "nr_products": 1950, "level": -1, "url": "http://www.newegg.com/Mice/SubCategory/ID-65", "text": "Mice", "department_url": "http://www.newegg.com/PCs-Laptops/Store", "description_title": "Wireless Mice, Optical Mice, Laser Mice and Trackball Mice", "parent_url": "http://www.newegg.com/Laptop-Accessories/Category/ID-26", "keyword_count": {"wireless": 4, "mice": 3}, "description_wc": 113, "description_text": "Use this link for more information on Computer Mice in our Learning Center At Newegg you can choose from a massive selection of computer mice from industry leading manufacturers including wired and wireless products, as well as sleek space-saving designs for notebook computers and ergonomic mice for the utmost in user comfort and gaming performance regardless of hand-orientation. Brands featured at Newegg include Microsoft, Kensington, Logitech, Targus and others in configurations of RF wireless, Fast RF wireless, Bluetooth Wireless, and standard PS/2 and USB wired interfaces. With a mouse to fit every computer performance need Newegg has what you need. For more information, please see our Computer Mouse Buying Guide.", "parent_text": "Laptop Accessories", "keyword_density": {"wireless": "3.5", "mice": "2.7"}, "department_id": 3},
{"nr_products": 226, "level": -1, "url": "http://www.newegg.com/Product/ProductList.aspx?Submit=Property&Subcategory=147&Description=&Type=&N=100007611&IsNodeId=1&IsPowerSearch=1&srchInDesc=&MinPrice=&MaxPrice=&PropertyCodeValue=524%3A47498&PropertyCodeValue=524%3A30386&PropertyCodeValue=524%3A30292&PropertyCodeValue=524%3A30548&PropertyCodeValue=524%3A38355&cm_sp=Memory17-_-VisNav-_-PerfGame", "text": "Desktop Memory", "department_url": "http://www.newegg.com/PCs-Laptops/Store", "description_wc": 0, "parent_url": "http://www.newegg.com/Store/PromotionStore/ID-2125620?name=Gaming-Entertainment", "parent_text": "Gaming Desktops", "department_text": "PCs & Laptops", "department_id": 3},
{"department_text": "PCs & Laptops", "level": -1, "url": "http://www.newegg.com/Laptop-Accessories/Category/ID-26", "text": "Laptop Accessories", "department_url": "http://www.newegg.com/PCs-Laptops/Store", "description_title": "Laptop Accessories", "parent_url": "http://www.newegg.com/Gaming-Notebooks/Category/ID-363", "keyword_count": {"laptop accessories": 3, "laptop": 14}, "description_wc": 378, "description_text": "It seems like everyone has a laptop these days. While tablets may be lighter, depending on the specific make and model, almost no device can match the functionality and convenience of a portable computer. Buying the right laptop accessories could create an even better user experience by making devices safer and supplementing the hardware. One of a laptop's biggest conveniences is its portability, but it can be awkward to carry in hand and doing so increases the odds of an accident - like being dropped on the sidewalk. A padded backpack can carry a laptop of any size while protecting the device from the elements. Laptop bags and cases are designed to absorb most bumps and bruises, so any valuables stored inside are less likely to be damaged during transit. You might also want to protect your laptop from potential thieves. Putting a lock on a computer would make it difficult for anyone to just walk away with it. Many laptops come with a security slot, so you might want to take advantage of it for additional security measures. Heavier users may find it difficult to find a device that can meet all their demands. A laptop battery can lose power quickly when the machine is asked to handle too many tasks at once. Sometimes there might not be an available outlet, so a power adapter is necessary to provide the extra juice needed to finish an important project before the charge dies. Additionally, most batteries last longer if a laptop does not overheat. Unfortunately, it's easy for a system's internal fan to be obstructed because they are mostly located on the bottom. A cooling pad could supplement a laptop's fans and prevent damage caused by excessive heat. Most of these devices connect via a USB port but have additional outlets so users can still connect flash drives with their computer while the cooling pad is working. Newegg is proud to offer a variety of laptop accessories, including laptop batteries, AC adapters, extended warranties, add-on cards, laptop bags and cases, hard drives, memory, networking devices, luggage & bags, replicators, docking stations and solid state disks. Find the laptop accessories you\u2019re looking for while enjoying the smoothest, most pleasurable online shopping experience available at Newegg.com.", "parent_text": "Gaming Notebooks", "keyword_density": {"laptop accessories": "1.6", "laptop": "3.7"}, "department_id": 3},
{"department_text": "PCs & Laptops", "nr_products": 505, "level": -1, "url": "http://www.newegg.com/PC-Games/SubCategory/ID-372", "text": "PC Games", "department_url": "http://www.newegg.com/PCs-Laptops/Store", "description_title": "PC Games", "parent_url": "http://www.newegg.com/Store/PromotionStore/ID-2125620?name=Gaming-Entertainment", "keyword_count": {"pc games": 2, "games": 11}, "description_wc": 314, "description_text": "While the video games available for various consoles may sometimes steal the spotlight, PC games still command the attention of millions of gamers all over the world. In the past year, numerous high-profile titles have been released to wide acclaim from both critics and casual players. That said, plenty of computer gamers are just as dedicated to the classics - if not more so - than the newest games available. Luckily, we've got classics, new favorites and everything in between. Fans of first-person shooters or similarly combat-heavy games will certainly have plenty of options on their hands. As far as genres go, these action-packed titles run the gamut from Renaissance-era swashbuckling and sci-fi dystopia to modern warfare and crime sagas. Additionally, intense role-playing games (RPGs) and real-time strategy (RTS) titles are available. Options in this category include games from established franchises like Diablo, Starcraft and Age of Empires to newer favorite series such as Fallout and The Elder Scrolls. However, those games aren't for everyone, and some are rated either T for Teen or M for Mature - intended for adults and teenagers of a certain age and maturity level. Parents, never fear - we've got plenty of other options for younger gamers and those uninterested in combat. These also encompass a wide variety of genres, as you could be creating entire new worlds in games like The Sims, planning culinary domination in Restaurant Empire or testing your wits with puzzle- and gambling-themed titles. You'll even have no trouble finding sports games or options that are suitable for even the youngest players. Our wide stock and affordable pricing - many titles are under $20 and even some newer computer games are well below their original MSRP - guarantees you'll be able to find the PC games best suited to your tastes, as well as your wallet!", "parent_text": "Gaming Desktops", "keyword_density": {"pc games": "1.3", "games": "3.5"}, "department_id": 3},
