{"department_text": "PCs & Laptops", "nr_products": 151, "level": -2, "url": "http://www.newegg.com/Replicators-Docking-Stations/SubCategory/ID-537", "text": "Replicators / Docking Stations", "department_url": "http://www.newegg.com/PCs-Laptops/Store", "description_title": "Laptop Docking Stations", "parent_url": "http://www.newegg.com/Laptop-Accessories/Category/ID-26", "keyword_count": {"laptop docking stations": 1, "laptop": 7, "docking": 3, "docking stations": 2, "stations": 3}, "description_wc": 288, "description_text": "Laptops and tablets have become popular options for shoppers who want to bring their computers everywhere. Manufacturers have begun producing slimmer models of both devices at the expense of some features that users may need, like ethernet jacks or HDMI ports. For those who have replaced their desktop with a laptop or tablet, this lack of hardware support can be a problem. Attaching a device to a port replicator is a solution for those who need the extra outlets and hardware support. Port replicators connect to a laptop or tablet via the battery hook-up, so the peripheral acts as a base for the device. Some tablet stations include an external keyboard for consumers who don't like typing on the screen, while others may need extra USB slots to connect with other accessories. Many ultrabooks don't have a CD drive, but some laptop docking stations have disc readers if you need to access content from CDs and DVDs. Other models offer ethernet connections, USB ports and audio jacks but lack a disc reader. You can pick and choose which features you need to supplement your laptop's functionality. Port replicators can be quickly disconnected so a device is never tethered to a desk. Users can connect all peripheral devices, like external hard drives and printers, to a base so instead of unplugging multiple accessories only the docking station needs to be removed from a tablet or laptop. This convenient accessory is great for workers who bring their mobile computers to work each day. A slim device doesn't have to lack the functionality found in desktops and heavier machines. Docking stations provide users with all the features missing from their laptops and tablets without sacrificing mobility.", "parent_text": "Laptop Accessories", "keyword_density": {"laptop docking stations": "1.0", "laptop": "2.4", "docking": "1.0", "docking stations": "1.4", "stations": "1.0"}, "department_id": 3},
{"department_text": "PCs & Laptops", "nr_products": 1950, "level": -2, "url": "http://www.newegg.com/Mice/SubCategory/ID-65", "text": "Mice", "department_url": "http://www.newegg.com/PCs-Laptops/Store", "description_title": "Wireless Mice, Optical Mice, Laser Mice and Trackball Mice", "parent_url": "http://www.newegg.com/Laptop-Accessories/Category/ID-26", "keyword_count": {"wireless": 4, "mice": 3}, "description_wc": 113, "description_text": "Use this link for more information on Computer Mice in our Learning Center At Newegg you can choose from a massive selection of computer mice from industry leading manufacturers including wired and wireless products, as well as sleek space-saving designs for notebook computers and ergonomic mice for the utmost in user comfort and gaming performance regardless of hand-orientation. Brands featured at Newegg include Microsoft, Kensington, Logitech, Targus and others in configurations of RF wireless, Fast RF wireless, Bluetooth Wireless, and standard PS/2 and USB wired interfaces. With a mouse to fit every computer performance need Newegg has what you need. For more information, please see our Computer Mouse Buying Guide.", "parent_text": "Laptop Accessories", "keyword_density": {"wireless": "3.5", "mice": "2.7"}, "department_id": 3},
