card, these units are installed internally but have an external attachment intended for a wired connection. You should make sure the wireless card you're thinking about purchasing matches your computer's hardware specifications. Access points must have driver support to function properly, so be sure to check what your system is capable of supporting.", "parent_text": "Laptop Accessories", "keyword_density": {"wireless": "2.2", "cards": "1.3", "laptop": "1.9", "wireless cards": "1.3", "laptop wireless cards": "1.0"}, "department_id": 3},
