{"department_text": "PCs & Laptops", "nr_products": 347, "level": -2, "url": "http://www.newegg.com/CD-DVD-Printers/SubCategory/ID-299", "text": "CD / DVD Printers", "department_url": "http://www.newegg.com/PCs-Laptops/Store", "description_title": "Printers & Multifunction Devices", "parent_url": "http://www.newegg.com/Printers-Scanners-Supplies/Category/ID-33", "keyword_count": {"printers": 5, "multifunction devices": 1}, "description_wc": 220, "description_text": "Use this link for more information on Printers and Multifunction Devices in our Learning Center Thinking about printing color photos and text documents in the comfort of your own living room or office? Newegg.com provides an extensive selection of ink jet and laser printers, as well as compact photo printers and all-in-one units (Fax/scanner/printer) from a portfolio of established manufacturers, from HP and Xerox, to Samsung, Canon, Brother, Epson, Kodak, Okidata, Panasonic and more to make sure you find the printer that most closely meets your requirements. In choosing a printer, you need to determine first what your main use will be. If it's text documents, it's one sort; if photos and brochures, something else. Think about the size of the documents you'll be printing -- letter and legal can be handled by almost all of them, but if you need a printer that can handle tabloid or larger jobs, you'll need something more powerful. Specialty photo printers offer a compact alternative if all you're doing is making copies of pix from your digital camera. Consider whether you need a networked or workgroup printer, capable of handling input from a number of computers. The All-in-One printers/scanner/fax machines offer a collection of services in one versatile yet compact machine.", "parent_text": "Printers / Scanners & Supplies", "keyword_density": {"multifunction devices": "0.9", "printers": "2.3"}, "department_id": 3},
