{"department_text": "PCs & Laptops", "level": -2, "url": "http://www.newegg.com/Projectors/Category/ID-343", "text": "Projectors", "department_url": "http://www.newegg.com/PCs-Laptops/Store", "description_title": "Business Projectors", "parent_url": "http://www.newegg.com/Ultrabooks/Category/ID-259", "keyword_count": {"business": 2, "projectors": 5, "business projectors": 1}, "description_wc": 136, "description_text": "Use this link for more on Business Projectors in our Learning Center Newegg.com offers a rich selection of projectors using LCD or DLP and from mainstream to professional.We carry projectors from Epson, InFocus, Mitsubishi, Sony, NEC and others. These days, projectors come in a wide range of resolutions and luminosities, for small offices or large lecture halls! Home and business users alike will be able to find projectors that fit and function perfectly both for the office and the home and enjoy maximum visual quality and impact as well as enhanced work efficiency. WARNING: Products with exposed solder may contain lead, a chemical known to the State of California to cause cancer, birth defects and other reproductive harm. Please wash hands after handling internal components and motherboards and avoid inhalation of fumes if heating the solder.", "parent_text": "Ultrabooks", "keyword_density": {"business projectors": "1.5", "projectors": "3.7", "business": "1.5"}, "department_id": 3},
