{"department_text": "PCs & Laptops", "nr_products": 151, "level": -3, "url": "http://www.newegg.com/Replicators-Docking-Stations/SubCategory/ID-537", "text": "Replicators / Docking Stations", "department_url": "http://www.newegg.com/PCs-Laptops/Store", "description_title": "Laptop Docking Stations", "parent_url": "http://www.newegg.com/Laptop-Accessories/Category/ID-26?name=Ultrabook-Accessories", "keyword_count": {"laptop docking stations": 1, "laptop": 7, "docking": 3, "docking stations": 2, "stations": 3}, "description_wc": 288, "description_text": "Laptops and tablets have become popular options for shoppers who want to bring their computers everywhere. Manufacturers have begun producing slimmer models of both devices at the expense of some features that users may need, like ethernet jacks or HDMI ports. For those who have replaced their desktop with a laptop or tablet, this lack of hardware support can be a problem. Attaching a device to a port replicator is a solution for those who need the extra outlets and hardware support. Port replicators connect to a laptop or tablet via the battery hook-up, so the peripheral acts as a base for the device. Some tablet stations include an external keyboard for consumers who don't like typing on the screen, while others may need extra USB slots to connect with other accessories. Many ultrabooks don't have a CD drive, but some laptop docking stations have disc readers if you need to access content from CDs and DVDs. Other models offer ethernet connections, USB ports and audio jacks but lack a disc reader. You can pick and choose which features you need to supplement your laptop's functionality. Port replicators can be quickly disconnected so a device is never tethered to a desk. Users can connect all peripheral devices, like external hard drives and printers, to a base so instead of unplugging multiple accessories only the docking station needs to be removed from a tablet or laptop. This convenient accessory is great for workers who bring their mobile computers to work each day. A slim device doesn't have to lack the functionality found in desktops and heavier machines. Docking stations provide users with all the features missing from their laptops and tablets without sacrificing mobility.", "parent_text": "Ultrabook Accessories", "keyword_density": {"laptop docking stations": "1.0", "laptop": "2.4", "docking": "1.0", "docking stations": "1.4", "stations": "1.0"}, "department_id": 3},
{"department_text": "PCs & Laptops", "nr_products": 483, "level": -3, "url": "http://www.newegg.com/Laptop-Memory/SubCategory/ID-381", "text": "Laptop Memory", "department_url": "http://www.newegg.com/PCs-Laptops/Store", "description_title": "Laptop / Notebook Memory", "parent_url": "http://www.newegg.com/Laptop-Accessories/Category/ID-26?name=Ultrabook-Accessories", "keyword_count": {"laptop notebook": 1, "notebook": 2, "notebook memory": 1, "memory": 7}, "description_wc": 196, "description_text": "Use this link for more information on Notebook Memory in our Learning Center Prefer to run your computer with fewer restrictions? You can do this and run more programs simultaneously by adding more memory to your system. The memory referred to here is RAM (Random Access Memory), which is essentially the computer's workspace - the place where your computer temporarily stores data and programs. Memory performance is an important factor influencing total system performance as memory speed allows more data to be transferred in a given time for greater system response and performance in demanding applications and games. With prices for memory falling there is no better time to stock up and at Newegg you can select from a wide assortment of speeds and capacity. Whether it's 125MB, 256MB, 512MB, 1GB or 2GB in capacity or speeds covering PC 100, PC 133, DDR 266 (PC 2100), DDR 333 (PC 2700), DDR 400 (PC 3200), DDR2 400 (PC2 3200), DDR2 533 (PC2 4200), DDR2 667 (PC2 5300), DDR2 667 (PC2 5400), DDR2 800 (PC2 6400) and more we have the right solution for your laptop / notebook upgrade needs.", "parent_text": "Ultrabook Accessories", "keyword_density": {"laptop notebook": "1.1", "notebook": "1.1", "notebook memory": "1.1", "memory": "3.7"}, "department_id": 3},
