at guide amateurs through the installation process step-by-step so they don't accidentally damage their system. Upgrading to a solid state drive from a hard drive can make any computer more efficient and convenient to use.", "parent_text": "Laptop Accessories", "keyword_density": {"solid state": "1.3", "drives": "2.3", "solid state drives": "1.0"}, "department_id": 3},
