{"department_text": "PCs & Laptops", "nr_products": 46, "level": -1, "url": "http://www.newegg.com/Tablet-PCs/SubCategory/ID-407?name=Convertible-Tablets", "text": "Convertible Tablets", "department_url": "http://www.newegg.com/PCs-Laptops/Store", "description_title": "Tablet PCs and Computers", "parent_url": "http://www.newegg.com/Tablets/Category/ID-164", "keyword_count": {"tablet pcs": 1, "pcs": 2, "computers": 3, "tablet": 9}, "description_wc": 306, "description_text": "There was a time when people thought of tablets as little more than glorified e-readers. Today, however, the leading tablet computers can compete with laptops and PCs in many respects. Newer models, such as the ASUS TF700T , offer the option to use full keyboards for easier use, and some are even equipped with webcams. Their touch screens make them a user-friendly option, especially for those who don't consider themselves tech-savvy. As the capabilities of tablet pcs increase, so do the possibilities! With a pc tablet, an entire library of books is within your grasp. You can buy eBooks directly from sites like Amazon.com or rent them from your local library. Many of our tablet computers are equipped with Windows 7, which provides maximum efficiency, and increased memory means you\u2019ll be able to store more media. Are you a gamer? With a computer tablet you can play your favorite downloadables like Angry Birds or Battleheart, and numerous other entertainment platforms help keep you connected to all your favorite games, books, photos, docs and more! Looking for something to bring to the office? Some of our higher-end models are perfect for those who want the perfect professional tablet. Check your email, store and modify documents and access your personal calendar with just a few simple swipes across the screen. Their durability and small size make them perfect for airports, transit and office waiting rooms. Remain productive or simply never grow bored with one of these industry-leading tablet computers. Be sure to also check out the Ultrabook as another option for lightweight, portable computing. No matter what you\u2019re looking for, you\u2019re bound to find it within our wide selection of pc tablets. Check out your options using the \"Compare\" feature and find the one that\u2019s right for you!", "parent_text": "Tablets", "keyword_density": {"tablet pcs": "0.7", "pcs": "0.7", "computers": "1.0", "tablet": "3.0"}, "department_id": 3},
{"department_text": "PCs & Laptops", "nr_products": 151, "level": -1, "url": "http://www.newegg.com/Replicators-Docking-Stations/SubCategory/ID-537", "text": "Replicators / Docking Stations", "department_url": "http://www.newegg.com/PCs-Laptops/Store", "description_title": "Laptop Docking Stations", "parent_url": "http://www.newegg.com/Laptop-Accessories/Category/ID-26", "keyword_count": {"laptop docking stations": 1, "laptop": 7, "docking": 3, "docking stations": 2, "stations": 3}, "description_wc": 288, "description_text": "Laptops and tablets have become popular options for shoppers who want to bring their computers everywhere. Manufacturers have begun producing slimmer models of both devices at the expense of some features that users may need, like ethernet jacks or HDMI ports. For those who have replaced their desktop with a laptop or tablet, this lack of hardware support can be a problem. Attaching a device to a port replicator is a solution for those who need the extra outlets and hardware support. Port replicators connect to a laptop or tablet via the battery hook-up, so the peripheral acts as a base for the device. Some tablet stations include an external keyboard for consumers who don't like typing on the screen, while others may need extra USB slots to connect with other accessories. Many ultrabooks don't have a CD drive, but some laptop docking stations have disc readers if you need to access content from CDs and DVDs. Other models offer ethernet connections, USB ports and audio jacks but lack a disc reader. You can pick and choose which features you need to supplement your laptop's functionality. Port replicators can be quickly disconnected so a device is never tethered to a desk. Users can connect all peripheral devices, like external hard drives and printers, to a base so instead of unplugging multiple accessories only the docking station needs to be removed from a tablet or laptop. This convenient accessory is great for workers who bring their mobile computers to work each day. A slim device doesn't have to lack the functionality found in desktops and heavier machines. Docking stations provide users with all the features missing from their laptops and tablets without sacrificing mobility.", "parent_text": "Laptop Accessories", "keyword_density": {"laptop docking stations": "1.0", "laptop": "2.4", "docking": "1.0", "docking stations": "1.4", "stations": "1.0"}, "department_id": 3},
