{"department_text": "Electronics", "level": 0, "url": "http://www.newegg.com/Tablets/Category/ID-164", "text": "Tablets", "department_url": "http://www.newegg.com/Electronics/Store", "description_title": "Tablets and Accessories", "parent_url": "http://www.newegg.com/Electronics/Store", "keyword_count": {"tablets": 5, "accessories": 4}, "description_wc": 283, "description_text": "Tablets combine the computing power of laptops with the mobility of smartphones, and the gadgets are lightweight and convenient. There are two operating systems - Windows 8 RT and Android - that make tablets even more functional by increasing processor speed and available options. Android tablets are consumer favorites because the software is very similar to the programs used on most smartphones. Users can add apps, games and features with only a couple of taps and gestures. Many people enjoy the familiarity and intuitive-nature of Android. You should always consider your options and find the device that is most suited for your needs. Windows 8 tablets are relatively new, but the devices combine popular features from Microsoft's operating system series with a mobile operating system. The tiled interface bears similarities to the Windows Phone, but it is more customizable and has a wider range of apps. Once you pick the perfect tablet, you'll need the right accessories. Detachable keyboards are a necessity if you want your mobile device to replace your laptop for all of your computing needs. The peripherals are very important if you buy a Windows 8 tablet so you can easily type in programs like Microsoft Word and Excel. Screen covers are among the most important tablet accessories. Tablets have large displays that are susceptible to scratches and scuff marks. You can either buy a plastic cover that blocks out dust or a protective sleeve that also saves prevents the bezel from damage. Some covers also feature keyboards so you can have two accessories in half the space. Accessories can make your tablet even more functional and help you replace your laptop or PC with a convenient mobile device.", "parent_text": "Electronics", "keyword_density": {"tablets": "1.8", "accessories": "1.4"}, "department_id": 4},
