{"department_text": "Electronics", "level": 0, "url": "http://www.newegg.com/Electronic-Gadgets/Category/ID-6", "text": "Electronic Gadgets", "department_url": "http://www.newegg.com/Electronics/Store", "description_title": "Electronic Gadgets", "parent_url": "http://www.newegg.com/Electronics/Store", "keyword_count": {"electronic gadgets": 1, "electronic": 2}, "description_wc": 179, "description_text": "Newegg is proud to offer a wide variety of electronic gadgets and gift ideas, as well. Our thousands of items include digital photo frames, Amplifiers, Acoustic Guitars, Electric Guitars, Controllers, Digital Pianos, Drums and Drum Sets, Keyboard Stands, Mixers and Mixer Accessories, Monitors, Music Archivers, Phono Accessories, Portable Keyboards, Portable PA Systems, Power Supplies, Preamplifiers, Signal Processors, Trainers, Turntables & Phonographs. Find the digital photo frames, musical instruments & accessories you're looking for at Newegg.com, and enjoy the smoothest, most pleasurable online shopping experience you can find. Digital Photo Frames Digital photo frames are a consumer electronic device designed to display digital photos without use of a computer. A digital photo frame is composed of three main parts: the LCD-panel, the PCB (Printed Circuit Board) and the outside frame. Some of the digital photo frames support movie clips, MP3 audios and JPEG pictures, while some of the digital photo frames support JPEGs only. Customers can upload their photos to a digital photo frame via a USB port. Digital photo frames also can display pictures directly from a memory card.", "parent_text": "Electronics", "keyword_density": {"electronic gadgets": "1.1", "electronic": "1.1"}, "department_id": 4},
{"department_text": "Electronics", "level": 0, "url": "http://www.newegg.com/Car-Electronics/Category/ID-283", "text": "Car Electronics", "department_url": "http://www.newegg.com/Electronics/Store", "description_title": "Car Electronics", "parent_url": "http://www.newegg.com/Electronics/Store", "keyword_count": {"car": 8, "electronics": 2, "car electronics": 1}, "description_wc": 65, "description_text": "Newegg is proud to offer a wide range of Automotive electronics, including Bluetooth cell phone accessories, car accessories, car amplifiers, car HD radios, car speakers, car stereos / CD changers, car subwoofers, car video units, GPS accessories, GPS navigation, satellite radio, radar detectors, rearview systems and professional installation. Newegg offer the latest car electronics with the best prices. Find everything you're looking for at Newegg.com!", "parent_text": "Electronics", "keyword_density": {"car": "12.3", "electronics": "3.1", "car electronics": "3.1"}, "department_id": 4},
