{"department_text": "Electronics", "level": 0, "url": "http://www.newegg.com/GPS-Accessories/Category/ID-277", "text": "GPS & Accessories", "department_url": "http://www.newegg.com/Electronics/Store", "description_title": "GPS Navigation Systems", "parent_url": "http://www.newegg.com/Electronics/Store", "keyword_count": {"navigation": 3, "gps navigation": 2, "systems": 1, "gps": 5}, "description_wc": 112, "description_text": "The Global Positioning System (GPS) is the only fully functional Global Navigation Satellite System (GNSS). Utilizing a constellation of at least 24 Medium Earth Orbit satellites that transmit precise microwave signals, the system enables a GPS receiver to determine its location, speed, direction, and time. GPS Navigation is used to help us see where we are right now, and to help us get from Point A to Point B. There are many manufacturers made for GPS Navigation, such as: Garmin, Magellan, TomTom, Mio, Navigon, Pharos, JENSEN, ASUS, Lowrance, Pioneer, Cobra, ,Plenio, DELPHI, Sony, Hewlett-Packard, Nextar, V7, HOLUX, Niko, VIAMICHELIN, Initial, Panasonic, XROAD, DeluoGPS and more. These are basically mapping systems.", "parent_text": "Electronics", "keyword_density": {"gps navigation": "3.6", "navigation": "2.7", "systems": "0.9", "gps": "4.5"}, "department_id": 4},
