{"department_text": "Electronics", "nr_products": 84, "level": 0, "url": "http://www.newegg.com/Blu-Ray-Players/SubCategory/ID-531", "text": "Blu-Ray Players", "department_url": "http://www.newegg.com/Electronics/Store", "description_title": "Blu-Ray Players", "parent_url": "http://www.newegg.com/Electronics/Store", "keyword_count": {"blu ray": 5, "players": 3, "blu ray players": 2}, "description_wc": 287, "description_text": "While DVD still occupies a certain portion of the home entertainment market, it's clear that Blu-ray will become an increasingly dominant format. If you're looking to enjoy your favorite high-powered action movies, raucous comedies and heartbreaking dramas in the best possible way, you'll thrill to the visual clarity and room-shaking sound that's available with the following Blu-ray players. Check out the players we have in stock and get started on your search! Many Blu-ray players now boast incredibly useful special features in addition to the astounding picture and sound quality available through their HDMI capabilities. Some include web browsers that connect through Wi-Fi, user interfaces that allow access to streaming video or music content through apps such as Netflix\u00ae, Hulu Plus\u00ae and Pandora\u00ae. In some models, content can be transferred from the player to a laptop, smartphone or tablet and playing it on the smaller device. Additionally, the average Blu-ray player often allows you to store music, video, photos and other media by uploading it via a USB device. Some - typically those on the moderate to high end of the price spectrum - are also programmed to be 3D capable and will produce even more stunning images when paired with an appropriately outfitted television. Sometimes, though, the most useful features are some of the simplest. With a typical Blu-ray player, one of its primary attributes is the ability to improve the audio and visual quality of the DVDs you use it to watch. This prevents you from having to get rid of your existing DVD collection, while also allowing you to experience all of those films and TV shows with enhanced picture and sound.", "parent_text": "Electronics", "keyword_density": {"blu ray": "3.5", "players": "1.1", "blu ray players": "2.1"}, "department_id": 4},
{"department_text": "Electronics", "level": -1, "url": "http://www.newegg.com/Projectors/Category/ID-343", "text": "Projectors", "department_url": "http://www.newegg.com/Electronics/Store", "description_title": "Business Projectors", "parent_url": "http://www.newegg.com/Tablets/Category/ID-164", "keyword_count": {"business": 2, "projectors": 5, "business projectors": 1}, "description_wc": 136, "description_text": "Use this link for more on Business Projectors in our Learning Center Newegg.com offers a rich selection of projectors using LCD or DLP and from mainstream to professional.We carry projectors from Epson, InFocus, Mitsubishi, Sony, NEC and others. These days, projectors come in a wide range of resolutions and luminosities, for small offices or large lecture halls! Home and business users alike will be able to find projectors that fit and function perfectly both for the office and the home and enjoy maximum visual quality and impact as well as enhanced work efficiency. WARNING: Products with exposed solder may contain lead, a chemical known to the State of California to cause cancer, birth defects and other reproductive harm. Please wash hands after handling internal components and motherboards and avoid inhalation of fumes if heating the solder.", "parent_text": "Tablets", "keyword_density": {"business projectors": "1.5", "projectors": "3.7", "business": "1.5"}, "department_id": 4},
{"department_text": "Electronics", "nr_products": 73, "level": 0, "url": "http://www.newegg.com/Home-Theater-Projectors/SubCategory/ID-513", "text": "Home Theater Projectors", "department_url": "http://www.newegg.com/Electronics/Store", "description_title": "Home Theater Projectors", "parent_url": "http://www.newegg.com/Electronics/Store", "keyword_count": {"home theater": 5, "projectors": 2}, "description_wc": 337, "description_text": "Putting together a home theater system can be difficult. All the equipment needs to be compatible to give an audience the best viewing experience. Due to strides in technology, audio devices can make movies and television shows sound crystal clear, but a standard high-definition television's picture might lag behind a sound system's performance. Buying the best home theater projector could level the playing field. If you're going to be watching a great deal of programming, a projector might be easier on the eyes than an LCD or LED television. The devices are backlit to create a sharper image on screen, while sending light directly into your vision. This is what usually causes eye strain after watching for an extended period of time. Projectors are only directing light toward the screen, making it more comfortable to enjoy a movie marathon. There is more flexibility with a home theater projector, as well. Instead of having a television with a set size, a projector can be adjusted to fill bigger and smaller display areas. Moving the device further away from the screen creates a bigger image, while moving it closer shrinks it. This is a convenient adjustment for users who want to use their device in more than one room. It is important to note the minimum and maximum size settings on each projector, because picture quality will deteriorate if moved beyond those thresholds. You may want to consider the lamp life of a projector before making a purchase. Light bulbs don't last forever, so at some point you'll need to replace one in your device. Most projectors offer settings designed to lengthen a bulb's life, but these options may reduce viewing quality while cutting down on power consumption. It's important to consider all your needs before buying a home theater projector. Make sure you have figured out what you expect from the device and what you'll use it for, so you can buy the best one for your home theater.", "parent_text": "Electronics", "keyword_density": {"home theater": "3.0", "projectors": "0.6"}, "department_id": 4},
