{"department_text": "Electronics", "level": -1, "url": "http://www.newegg.com/Camcorder-Accessories/Category/ID-5", "text": "Camcorder Accessories", "department_url": "http://www.newegg.com/Electronics/Store", "description_title": "Camcorders, Digital Camcorders and Analog Camcorders", "parent_url": "http://www.newegg.com/Digital-Cameras/Category/ID-354", "keyword_count": {"analog camcorders": 1, "digital": 1}, "description_wc": 143, "description_text": "Here at Newegg.com we offer a wide selection of camcorder products from the manufacturers you know and trust. We want our customers to own the camcorder that was made just for them. To do that, it is important to have at least a rudimentary understanding of camcorder features, specifications and technologies, which are explained in our Camcorder Buying Guide and recommended reading list. After that, just take a glance at our extensive listing of camcorder product specifications while browsing. Shopping at Newegg.com just got happier! Use this link for more information on Digital and Analog Camcorders in our Learning Center WARNING: Products with exposed solder may contain lead, a chemical known to the State of California to cause cancer, birth defects and other reproductive harm. Please wash hands after handling internal components and motherboards and avoid inhalation of fumes if heating the solder.", "parent_text": "Digital Cameras", "keyword_density": {"analog camcorders": "1.4", "digital": "0.7"}, "department_id": 4},
{"department_text": "Electronics", "nr_products": 134, "level": -1, "url": "http://www.newegg.com/Digital-Photo-Frames/SubCategory/ID-548", "text": "Digital Photo Frames", "department_url": "http://www.newegg.com/Electronics/Store", "description_title": "Digital photo frames", "parent_url": "http://www.newegg.com/Digital-Cameras/Category/ID-354", "keyword_count": {"frames": 11, "photo": 9, "digital photo frames": 5, "digital": 8}, "description_wc": 223, "description_text": "Digital photo frames typically display the pictures directly from a camera's memory card, though some frames also provide internal memory storage. Certain frames allow users to directly upload pictures to the frame's memory via a USB connection. However, few digital photo frames have built-in memory and due the high price of built-in memory this feature has been seen mostly on high-end frames, and the memory provided has been relatively small. All digital photo frames can display JPEG pictures on its screen. Most will display the photos as a slideshow, usually with an adjustable time interval. Some can also send photos to your printer. However, others support additional multimedia content, including movie clips recorded in a digital camera's movie mode, MPEG video files and/or MP3 audio, set as soundtrack to your slideshow. Certain frames can also load pictures over the Internet from RSS feeds, photo sharing sites such as Flickr, Picasa, FrameChannel and even from e-mail. Such networked models usually support wireless (802.11) connections. Other ones can display .txt files. Digital photo frames represent an advance on the old paper photo albums, because you don\u2019t have to pull them off the shelf to look at them, and they\u2019ll turn the pages for you! Newegg Offers Discount Digital frames, Digital photo frames, Digital picture frames", "parent_text": "Digital Cameras", "keyword_density": {"frames": "4.9", "photo": "4.0", "digital photo frames": "6.7", "digital": "3.6"}, "department_id": 4},
