{"department_text": "Electronics", "nr_products": 108, "level": -1, "url": "http://www.newegg.com/Portable-DVD-Players/SubCategory/ID-491", "text": "Portable DVD Players", "department_url": "http://www.newegg.com/Electronics/Store", "description_title": "Portable DVD Players", "parent_url": "http://www.newegg.com/Portable-Devices/Category/ID-8", "keyword_count": {"portable": 5, "portable dvd players": 2, "portable dvd": 3}, "description_wc": 326, "description_text": "Ever want to watch a movie when you're away from home, but you don't have Internet access for your computer or feel like lugging an entertainment system with you? There are portable devices at the ready to help meet your movie-watching needs with much less weight and more convenience than trying to jerry-rig conventional devices into a road-ready solution. A portable DVD player can hook up to any television with the right wires for immediate playback. Some are even equipped with Blu-ray technology, meaning you aren't limited to standard video quality if you purchase the right utility. These devices also have built-in screens, so if there's no TV present or the picture isn't good enough, you can just watch right on the device itself. What's more, portable DVD players are small, lightweight and compact, making them great for airplane and train travel. Some devices are so slim as to seem like tablet computers, while others feature multiple screens. One device holds the disk while the other maintains a wireless signal, allowing for several people to share the same viewing experience without everyone having to crowd around a single screen. Other models receive television signals and basic programming, while still others also come equipped for CD playback with built-in stereo speakers. These rigs look more like old-school boomboxes, but are still just as portable and multi-functional as their much slimmer brethren. Trading in profile for power, these devices provide far superior audio playback and can function as more than just a movie system, making it more of a full entertainment device that could be great for a child's room or a summer camp house. Great for home or on-the-go, portable DVD players allow for film viewing anywhere and anytime. Light, powerful and flexible, they are the perfect tool to round out a complete media experience, regardless of where you go.", "parent_text": "Portable Devices", "keyword_density": {"portable dvd": "1.8", "portable": "1.5", "portable dvd players": "1.8"}, "department_id": 4},
