{"department_text": "Cell Phones & Cell Phone Accessories", "level": -1, "url": "http://www.newegg.com/Bluetooth-Headset-Accessories/Category/ID-247", "text": "Bluetooth Headset & Accessories", "department_url": "http://www.newegg.com/Cell-Phones-Cell-Phone-Accessories/Store/ID-140", "description_title": "Bluetooth Headsets and Accessories", "parent_url": "http://www.newegg.com/Apple-iPhone-5/PromotionStore/ID-144?name=Apple-iPhone-Store", "keyword_count": {"headsets": 2, "bluetooth headsets": 1, "accessories": 3, "bluetooth": 9}, "description_wc": 302, "description_text": "Bluetooth technology allows you to increase the functionality of most mobile devices. Many smartphones and MP3 players have weak internal speakers, which produce low quality audio and distorted sounds. Fortunately, most gadgets can be wirelessly synced with Bluetooth headsets and speakers that offer strong audio performance. Many consumers were introduced to Bluetooth technology by the hands-free headsets some drivers used. The devices are convenient to set up and are much safer to use than answering the phone while behind the wheel. There are models that resemble older versions and are simple earpieces so you don't have to hold your smartphone. Alternatively, there are new Bluetooth accessories that connect your car's sound system with your cell phone. You simply plug the receiver into your vehicle's auxiliary jack and then pair it with your mobile device. The gadget can be placed on your wheel so that you never have to let go while driving when your phone rings. Other Bluetooth accessories can make your smartphone or MP3 player easier to use by eliminating wires. Instead of using traditional headphones, you can sync your device with a wireless model thanks to Bluetooth technology. These types of headphones can be especially useful during workouts when annoying cords can hinder certain motions. Bluetooth speakers allow you to play your favorite songs from your mobile device without having to leave it on a dock or tether it to your stereo. Simply pair your sound system with your smartphone and you can fill any room with your music. One of the benefits of using Bluetooth speakers is that you can move around with your gadget without hurting the connection. Most Bluetooth accessories are compatible with every mobile operating system, so you can find the right gadget whether you have the iPhone 5 or a BlackBerry.", "parent_text": "Apple iPhone Store", "keyword_density": {"headsets": "0.7", "bluetooth": "3.0", "accessories": "1.0", "bluetooth headsets": "0.7"}, "department_id": 7},
