{"department_text": "Electronics", "nr_products": 18, "level": -1, "url": "http://www.newegg.com/TV-Combos/SubCategory/ID-512", "text": "TV Combos", "department_url": "http://www.newegg.com/Electronics/Store", "description_title": "TV DVD Combo", "parent_url": "http://www.newegg.com/Televisions/Category/ID-264", "keyword_count": {"tv": 4, "dvd": 6, "tv dvd combo": 2}, "description_wc": 275, "description_text": "Watching television is great, but having to turn on a separate DVD player for your favorite films and handle separate remote controls can be an annoyance. You may also want to save space in your entertainment unit for other devices like audio tuners and video game consoles. The best solution for size and convenience is a TV DVD combo that puts both utilities into a single device. These devices come in a variety of sizes and styles similar to any conventional television, save that they have a DVD player built right into the screen. One remote control is all that's needed to switch between regular cable and movie viewing. Some units are also equipped with radio tuners and under-shelf installation kits for kitchen use or other areas with minimal shelf space, enhancing flexibility and maximizing room usage. Built-in players can be standard DVD or Blu-ray, depending on the model purchased. LCD and HD displays are another variable to decide upon before making a purchase. There's no difference in picture quality between a standard television and one with DVD capability, so approaching it like a regular TV purchase with added usability is one perk to picking this multi-faceted device. They have all the same connectivity and require no different cables than a standard television, meaning it's no extra investment if you are just replacing a couple of existing devices to save space. Functional, flexible and fun, TV DVD combo devices provide the best of both movies and TV without having to switch remotes. These offer a great way to increase storage space without taking away from the entertainment experience.", "parent_text": "Televisions", "keyword_density": {"tv": "1.5", "dvd": "2.2", "tv dvd combo": "2.2"}, "department_id": 4},
