{"department_text": "Electronics", "nr_products": 1568, "level": -3, "url": "http://www.newegg.com/HDMI-Cables/SubCategory/ID-2809", "text": "HDMI Cables", "department_url": "http://www.newegg.com/Electronics/Store", "description_title": "HDMI Cables", "parent_url": "http://www.newegg.com/Audio-Video-Cables/Category/ID-184", "keyword_count": {"cables": 7, "hdmi": 8, "hdmi cables": 3}, "description_wc": 368, "description_text": "The visual perks of HD video in high resolution formats such as 1080p can turn your favorite movies - even those you've seen a dozen times - into entirely new, fresh experiences. However, you need a proper HDMI cable to complete the connection between your television and cable box, game console, DVD or Blu-ray player. Luckily for you, we've got a wide range of HDMI cables in stock. These range from affordable models priced at bargain rates to high-end Monster HDMI cable as well as those made by Cables to Go and other top-tier names in the industry, all of which have been engineered with the finest precision. Take a look at our selection and choose for yourself! If you're looking for a simple, straightforward and affordable HDMI to DVI cable, you won't be disappointed with what you find in our selection. Cables for this purpose with notably low prices are available from manufacturers including Rosewill, Kaybles, Nippon Labs, Link Depot, Bytecc and many others. These will be compatible with DVD and Blu-ray players, HDTV receivers, projectors and A/V receivers - essentially, any device for which you need to provide HDMI connectivity. True audiophiles and movie buffs will not be satisfied with the quality of a standard HDMI cable, and may want to try one of the high-end cables made by Monster or Cables To Go. Though these are priced according to high-end standards, you'll certainly get nothing less than what you pay for in terms of quality. Constructed of fine materials including 24-karat gold-plated connectors, silver-coated oxygen-free (OFC) conductors and nitrogen-injected gas dielectric to ensure durability, signal strength and visual quality, these are certain to produce a crisp image and powerful sound. You can find models that occupy a middle ground between upscale quality and affordability, and if you need HDMI cables for specific purposes, such as connecting to a camcorder or an Ethernet IP enabled device, those are available as well. By choosing one of our many HDMI cables, you'll be sure to get the best visual bang for your buck while experiencing your favorite movies, TV shows and video games.", "parent_text": "Audio / Video Cables", "keyword_density": {"cables": "1.9", "hdmi": "2.2", "hdmi cables": "1.6"}, "department_id": 4},
