{"department_text": "Cell Phones & Cell Phone Accessories", "level": 0, "url": "http://www.newegg.com/Cell-Phones-Unlocked/Category/ID-249", "text": "Cell Phones - Unlocked", "department_url": "http://www.newegg.com/Cell-Phones-Cell-Phone-Accessories/Store/ID-140", "description_title": "Unlocked Mobile Phones", "parent_url": "http://www.newegg.com/Cell-Phones-Cell-Phone-Accessories/Store/ID-140", "keyword_count": {"phones": 6, "unlocked": 6}, "description_wc": 292, "description_text": "An unlocked phone can offer features that are unavailable on locked devices. Shoppers choose to buy unlocked phones when they want to use a new carrier, customize their gadgets or use models that aren't offered by their service providers. Network carriers can't sell certain devices because of contractual restrictions which can frustrate their subscribers. Aside from leaving the coverage company, buying an unlocked phone is consumers' only option when they want to use a device that a provider doesn't sell. Many of the most popular smartphones have been unlocked, and they can be synced with any signal. The iPhone 4S, iPhone 5 , Samsung Galaxy S3 and Sony Xperia S can all be obtained without having to sign up with a new carrier. Once you find the perfect device, you simply find your coverage provider's signal and tune your phone to its frequency. You can also find phones that are no longer manufactured. Instead of limiting yourself to touchscreen devices, you can find feature phones and QWERTY models that have been discontinued. Many of these phones are new so you don't have to worry about using a refurbished or damaged device. Unlocked phones can access most major carriers. Changing companies can help save you money by avoiding roaming charges while traveling abroad or out of your local coverage area. Additionally, you can bring your device anywhere instead of buying a new phone whenever you move to a location that isn't supported by your company. Unlocking your phone manually can be difficult. Without the proper training and technical skill, you can damage your phone and prevent it from working properly. Buying an unlocked phone eliminates all of the hassles so you can immediately begin using your device.", "parent_text": "Cell Phones & Cell Phone Accessories", "keyword_density": {"phones": "2.1", "unlocked": "2.1"}, "department_id": 7},
