{"department_text": "Electronics", "nr_products": 84, "level": -2, "url": "http://www.newegg.com/Blu-Ray-Players/SubCategory/ID-531?name=Blu-Ray-Players", "text": "Blu-Ray Players", "department_url": "http://www.newegg.com/Electronics/Store", "description_title": "Blu-Ray Players", "parent_url": "http://www.newegg.com/Televisions/Category/ID-264", "keyword_count": {"blu ray": 5, "players": 3, "blu ray players": 2}, "description_wc": 287, "description_text": "While DVD still occupies a certain portion of the home entertainment market, it's clear that Blu-ray will become an increasingly dominant format. If you're looking to enjoy your favorite high-powered action movies, raucous comedies and heartbreaking dramas in the best possible way, you'll thrill to the visual clarity and room-shaking sound that's available with the following Blu-ray players. Check out the players we have in stock and get started on your search! Many Blu-ray players now boast incredibly useful special features in addition to the astounding picture and sound quality available through their HDMI capabilities. Some include web browsers that connect through Wi-Fi, user interfaces that allow access to streaming video or music content through apps such as Netflix\u00ae, Hulu Plus\u00ae and Pandora\u00ae. In some models, content can be transferred from the player to a laptop, smartphone or tablet and playing it on the smaller device. Additionally, the average Blu-ray player often allows you to store music, video, photos and other media by uploading it via a USB device. Some - typically those on the moderate to high end of the price spectrum - are also programmed to be 3D capable and will produce even more stunning images when paired with an appropriately outfitted television. Sometimes, though, the most useful features are some of the simplest. With a typical Blu-ray player, one of its primary attributes is the ability to improve the audio and visual quality of the DVDs you use it to watch. This prevents you from having to get rid of your existing DVD collection, while also allowing you to experience all of those films and TV shows with enhanced picture and sound.", "parent_text": "Televisions", "keyword_density": {"blu ray": "3.5", "players": "1.1", "blu ray players": "2.1"}, "department_id": 4},
{"department_text": "Electronics", "nr_products": 168, "level": -2, "url": "http://www.newegg.com/Universal-Remotes/SubCategory/ID-283", "text": "Universal Remotes", "department_url": "http://www.newegg.com/Electronics/Store", "description_title": "Universal Remotes", "parent_url": "http://www.newegg.com/Televisions/Category/ID-264", "keyword_count": {"universal": 6, "universal remotes": 4, "remotes": 5}, "description_wc": 213, "description_text": "Universal Remotes allow you to control all your home entertainment equipment such as TV's, VCR players, DVD players, home theater receivers and more from just one device. Offering choices of Inferred, RF or a combination of both the universal remotes allow you to control your multiple equipment from across the room or even through walls (or people blocking your devices) depending on the set up of your system. No longer will you need to hunt for different remotes. Now all commands will be handled by just one simple to use device. How Universal Remotes Work Universal Remotes work by storing the commands for all your various equipment into one system. Programming can be as simple as downloading some software to your computer and inputting the brands and model numbers of the equipment you want to control via the universal remote. Once everything is configured the data is then downloaded into your new remote via a cable. Overall programming is quick and easy however more advanced options are available. Once you have made the jump to a Universal Remote you will wonder why you ever lived without. Simplicity couldn't be easier. Visit Newegg for all your home entertainment and computer needs. You'll find everything you need, so please come back often.", "parent_text": "Televisions", "keyword_density": {"universal": "2.8", "universal remotes": "3.8", "remotes": "2.3"}, "department_id": 4},
{"department_text": "Electronics", "nr_products": 18, "level": -2, "url": "http://www.newegg.com/TV-Combos/SubCategory/ID-512", "text": "TV Combos", "department_url": "http://www.newegg.com/Electronics/Store", "description_title": "TV DVD Combo", "parent_url": "http://www.newegg.com/Televisions/Category/ID-264", "keyword_count": {"tv": 4, "dvd": 6, "tv dvd combo": 2}, "description_wc": 275, "description_text": "Watching television is great, but having to turn on a separate DVD player for your favorite films and handle separate remote controls can be an annoyance. You may also want to save space in your entertainment unit for other devices like audio tuners and video game consoles. The best solution for size and convenience is a TV DVD combo that puts both utilities into a single device. These devices come in a variety of sizes and styles similar to any conventional television, save that they have a DVD player built right into the screen. One remote control is all that's needed to switch between regular cable and movie viewing. Some units are also equipped with radio tuners and under-shelf installation kits for kitchen use or other areas with minimal shelf space, enhancing flexibility and maximizing room usage. Built-in players can be standard DVD or Blu-ray, depending on the model purchased. LCD and HD displays are another variable to decide upon before making a purchase. There's no difference in picture quality between a standard television and one with DVD capability, so approaching it like a regular TV purchase with added usability is one perk to picking this multi-faceted device. They have all the same connectivity and require no different cables than a standard television, meaning it's no extra investment if you are just replacing a couple of existing devices to save space. Functional, flexible and fun, TV DVD combo devices provide the best of both movies and TV without having to switch remotes. These offer a great way to increase storage space without taking away from the entertainment experience.", "parent_text": "Televisions", "keyword_density": {"tv": "1.5", "dvd": "2.2", "tv dvd combo": "2.2"}, "department_id": 4},
{"department_text": "Cell Phones & Cell Phone Accessories", "level": -1, "url": "http://www.newegg.com/Bluetooth-Headsets-Accessories/Category/ID-247", "text": "Bluetooth Headsets & Accessories", "department_url": "http://www.newegg.com/Cell-Phones-Cell-Phone-Accessories/Store/ID-140", "description_title": "Bluetooth Headsets and Accessories", "parent_url": "http://www.newegg.com/Wired-Headsets-Speakers/Category/ID-350", "keyword_count": {"headsets": 2, "bluetooth headsets": 1, "accessories": 3, "bluetooth": 9}, "description_wc": 302, "description_text": "Bluetooth technology allows you to increase the functionality of most mobile devices. Many smartphones and MP3 players have weak internal speakers, which produce low quality audio and distorted sounds. Fortunately, most gadgets can be wirelessly synced with Bluetooth headsets and speakers that offer strong audio performance. Many consumers were introduced to Bluetooth technology by the hands-free headsets some drivers used. The devices are convenient to set up and are much safer to use than answering the phone while behind the wheel. There are models that resemble older versions and are simple earpieces so you don't have to hold your smartphone. Alternatively, there are new Bluetooth accessories that connect your car's sound system with your cell phone. You simply plug the receiver into your vehicle's auxiliary jack and then pair it with your mobile device. The gadget can be placed on your wheel so that you never have to let go while driving when your phone rings. Other Bluetooth accessories can make your smartphone or MP3 player easier to use by eliminating wires. Instead of using traditional headphones, you can sync your device with a wireless model thanks to Bluetooth technology. These types of headphones can be especially useful during workouts when annoying cords can hinder certain motions. Bluetooth speakers allow you to play your favorite songs from your mobile device without having to leave it on a dock or tether it to your stereo. Simply pair your sound system with your smartphone and you can fill any room with your music. One of the benefits of using Bluetooth speakers is that you can move around with your gadget without hurting the connection. Most Bluetooth accessories are compatible with every mobile operating system, so you can find the right gadget whether you have the iPhone 5 or a BlackBerry.", "parent_text": "Wired Headsets & Speakers", "keyword_density": {"headsets": "0.7", "bluetooth": "3.0", "accessories": "1.0", "bluetooth headsets": "0.7"}, "department_id": 7},
{"department_text": "Electronics", "nr_products": 168, "level": -2, "url": "http://www.newegg.com/Universal-Remotes/SubCategory/ID-283", "text": "Universal Remotes", "department_url": "http://www.newegg.com/Electronics/Store", "description_title": "Universal Remotes", "parent_url": "http://www.newegg.com/Home-Video-Accessories/Category/ID-358", "keyword_count": {"universal": 6, "universal remotes": 4, "remotes": 5}, "description_wc": 213, "description_text": "Universal Remotes allow you to control all your home entertainment equipment such as TV's, VCR players, DVD players, home theater receivers and more from just one device. Offering choices of Inferred, RF or a combination of both the universal remotes allow you to control your multiple equipment from across the room or even through walls (or people blocking your devices) depending on the set up of your system. No longer will you need to hunt for different remotes. Now all commands will be handled by just one simple to use device. How Universal Remotes Work Universal Remotes work by storing the commands for all your various equipment into one system. Programming can be as simple as downloading some software to your computer and inputting the brands and model numbers of the equipment you want to control via the universal remote. Once everything is configured the data is then downloaded into your new remote via a cable. Overall programming is quick and easy however more advanced options are available. Once you have made the jump to a Universal Remote you will wonder why you ever lived without. Simplicity couldn't be easier. Visit Newegg for all your home entertainment and computer needs. You'll find everything you need, so please come back often.", "parent_text": "Home Video Accessories", "keyword_density": {"universal": "2.8", "universal remotes": "3.8", "remotes": "2.3"}, "department_id": 4},
