{"department_text": "Gaming", "nr_products": 989, "level": 0, "url": "http://www.newegg.com/PS3-Accessories/SubCategory/ID-547?cm_sp=PS3Cat-_-VisNav-_-Accessories&name=PlayStation-Accessories", "text": "PlayStation Accessories", "department_url": "http://www.newegg.com/Gaming/Store", "description_title": "PS3 Accessories", "parent_url": "http://www.newegg.com/Gaming/Store", "keyword_count": {"ps3": 4, "ps3 accessories": 1, "accessories": 2}, "description_wc": 304, "description_text": "The PlayStation 3 is a multimedia hub that's well-suited to a wide range of users, even those who don't have an extensive video game collection. With streaming services, a built-in Blu-ray player and internet connectivity, there are plenty of ways you can stay entertained with Sony's console. Picking out the right PS3 accessories can create an even better experience while using the device, by enhancing all of its best features. A controller is a basic necessity for every user. Consoles typically only come with one, so having extra controllers is necessary if you want to invite friends to play a game. You can pick and choose from numerous colors. Don't forget to buy a charger, as well. PS3s sync with new controllers via the wired connection, and without it, once a battery dies it's dead for good. For people that use video services but have a hard time searching for movies and TV shows with the on-screen keyboard, there are external keyboards available. You won't have to navigate to different letters with the analog sticks after buying a mini-keyboard that syncs with your PS3. As the Blu-ray player was a major part of the PS3's appeal for many, a remote control may be more intuitive to use than controllers and make on-screen navigation much simpler. Additionally, movies will look even better with a HDMI cable for a higher resolution picture. For gamers who like to play online, a headset may be the perfect accessory to enhance the experience. You can use this tool to strategize with teammates or psych out an opponent during a heated basketball or football game. Buying the right PlayStation 3 accessories can make the console even more fun to use and enhance all your favorite features.", "parent_text": "Gaming", "keyword_density": {"ps3": "1.3", "ps3 accessories": "0.7", "accessories": "0.7"}, "department_id": 6},
