{"department_text": "Gaming", "nr_products": 505, "level": -1, "url": "http://www.newegg.com/PC-Games/SubCategory/ID-372", "text": "PC Games", "department_url": "http://www.newegg.com/Gaming/Store", "description_title": "PC Games", "parent_url": "http://www.newegg.com/PC-Games-Accessories/Category/ID-275", "keyword_count": {"pc games": 2, "games": 11}, "description_wc": 314, "description_text": "While the video games available for various consoles may sometimes steal the spotlight, PC games still command the attention of millions of gamers all over the world. In the past year, numerous high-profile titles have been released to wide acclaim from both critics and casual players. That said, plenty of computer gamers are just as dedicated to the classics - if not more so - than the newest games available. Luckily, we've got classics, new favorites and everything in between. Fans of first-person shooters or similarly combat-heavy games will certainly have plenty of options on their hands. As far as genres go, these action-packed titles run the gamut from Renaissance-era swashbuckling and sci-fi dystopia to modern warfare and crime sagas. Additionally, intense role-playing games (RPGs) and real-time strategy (RTS) titles are available. Options in this category include games from established franchises like Diablo, Starcraft and Age of Empires to newer favorite series such as Fallout and The Elder Scrolls. However, those games aren't for everyone, and some are rated either T for Teen or M for Mature - intended for adults and teenagers of a certain age and maturity level. Parents, never fear - we've got plenty of other options for younger gamers and those uninterested in combat. These also encompass a wide variety of genres, as you could be creating entire new worlds in games like The Sims, planning culinary domination in Restaurant Empire or testing your wits with puzzle- and gambling-themed titles. You'll even have no trouble finding sports games or options that are suitable for even the youngest players. Our wide stock and affordable pricing - many titles are under $20 and even some newer computer games are well below their original MSRP - guarantees you'll be able to find the PC games best suited to your tastes, as well as your wallet!", "parent_text": "PC Games & Accessories", "keyword_density": {"pc games": "1.3", "games": "3.5"}, "department_id": 6},
