{"department_text": "Gaming", "nr_products": 88, "level": -1, "url": "http://www.newegg.com/Nintendo-DS-Accessories/SubCategory/ID-244", "text": "Nintendo DS Accessories", "department_url": "http://www.newegg.com/Gaming/Store", "description_title": "Nintendo DS Accessories", "parent_url": "http://www.newegg.com/Nintendo-DS/Category/ID-401", "keyword_count": {"nintendo ds": 6, "nintendo ds accessories": 3, "accessories": 5, "ds": 10}, "description_wc": 169, "description_text": "Nintendo DS revolutionizes handheld gameplay. With two ultra bright screens, 3D graphics, touch-screen technology and wireless communication, you can challenge yourself or your friends anywhere, anytime. It's lightweight and compact for portability, and there are hundreds of complex and engaging games available. Nintendo DS Accessories Add Convenience While Nintendo DS is simple to transport, it's still inconvenient to carry it in your hands all day. Some Nintendo DS accessories make it possible to carry your system without holding it in your hands or stashing it in a bag. If you're taking your Nintendo DS on a trip, you'll want an easy way to transport it together with your games, accessories, and batteries. Here at Newegg, we sell various Nintendo DS accessories that will make life a little easier and maximize your enjoyment of this great video game system. With the widest selection of accessories at the best prices, we can help you make your gaming experience even better, on the road or at home.", "parent_text": "Nintendo DS", "keyword_density": {"nintendo ds": "7.1", "nintendo ds accessories": "5.3", "accessories": "3.0", "ds": "5.9"}, "department_id": 6},
{"department_text": "Gaming", "nr_products": 1163, "level": -1, "url": "http://www.newegg.com/Game-Boy-Games/SubCategory/ID-478", "text": "Game Boy Games", "department_url": "http://www.newegg.com/Gaming/Store", "description_title": "Game Boy Video Games", "parent_url": "http://www.newegg.com/Nintendo-DS/Category/ID-401", "keyword_count": {"game boy video games": 6, "video games": 7, "game": 24, "video": 8, "game boy": 10, "games": 11}, "description_wc": 250, "description_text": "Nothing rescues people from prolonged boredom quite like Game Boy video games, the perfect distraction when you're away from home and have nothing to do. The portability is what makes Game Boy so convenient, and the quality graphics and enjoyable games are what make it the most popular portable video game system on the market. There Are Game Boy Video Games for Everyone! The selection of Game Boy video games to choose from is incredibly diverse. Sports fans can enjoy numerous football, basketball, and baseball games. Game Boy may be small, but it can hold a considerable amount of memory. Some sports games feature entire professional leagues, all the players, and the attributes of each individual athlete. In addition to sports, there are many puzzle, adventure, and even educational Game Boy video games available. No matter which type you or your child want to play, we've got a game to match your interests. If you're searching for new video games to keep occupied, you've found the right place. Here at Newegg, we sell Game Boy video games at incredible prices, the lowest you'll find anywhere on the Internet. In addition to the latest and most popular Game Boy video games, we also offer a wide selection of Game Boy accessories. If you want to play your Game Boy games on your TV through your GameCube, we sell the player you'll need. We also offer storage devices, clips, charging stations, distortion-removing lenses, and more.", "parent_text": "Nintendo DS", "keyword_density": {"game boy video games": "9.6", "video games": "5.6", "game": "9.6", "video": "3.2", "game boy": "8.0", "games": "4.4"}, "department_id": 6},
