{"department_text": "Software", "nr_products": 103, "level": 0, "url": "http://www.newegg.com/Business-Finance/SubCategory/ID-523", "text": "Business & Finance", "department_url": "http://www.newegg.com/Software/Store", "description_title": "Business & Finance Software", "parent_url": "http://www.newegg.com/Software/Store", "keyword_count": {"finance software": 2, "business": 7, "software": 8}, "description_wc": 314, "description_text": "Technology has become an integral part of most small businesses. Programs have been intuitively designed for more efficient use by consumers. The right business software can help any establishment run more smoothly by eliminating some headaches caused by older software. Small business owners can make sure their staff has access to all the right equipment so their jobs are done well. For basic office functions there are standard document creation programs - including ones for text, spreadsheets and schedules. A company may work more efficiently if employees have familiar software available, instead of learning how to use an entirely new set of tools and features. If you want to focus on growing your business' online presence, there are programs available for website design. Pages can be created on site by your own employees, instead of outsourcing the project to a potentially expensive web developer. You'll also have better control over what content is available on your website due to such new software. Other programs are designed to make financial tasks easier and less time consuming. Currently, finance software titles that can handle everything from taxes to payroll and expenses to revenue are available. Finance software makes it possible for a business to perform its own bookkeeping and eliminates the need to hire outside consultants. Make sure you buy software that's compatible with all your computers' OS's. Many programs that work on a Windows-based PC won't work on a Mac and vice versa. This can also be a problem when trying to share documents - sometimes the formats aren't compatible from one OS to another, making files inaccessible to employees operating on different systems. The right business software can help any small business run just as efficiently as a large corporation. It's important to figure out what your company's computing needs are so you buy only the correct programs.", "parent_text": "Software", "keyword_density": {"finance software": "1.3", "business": "2.2", "software": "2.5"}, "department_id": 5},
