{"department_text": "Computer Hardware", "nr_products": 347, "level": -1, "url": "http://www.newegg.com/CD-DVD-Printers/SubCategory/ID-299", "text": "CD / DVD Printers", "department_url": "http://www.newegg.com/Computer-Hardware/Store", "description_title": "Printers & Multifunction Devices", "parent_url": "http://www.newegg.com/Printers-Scanners-Supplies/Category/ID-33", "keyword_count": {"printers": 5, "multifunction devices": 1}, "description_wc": 220, "description_text": "Use this link for more information on Printers and Multifunction Devices in our Learning Center Thinking about printing color photos and text documents in the comfort of your own living room or office? Newegg.com provides an extensive selection of ink jet and laser printers, as well as compact photo printers and all-in-one units (Fax/scanner/printer) from a portfolio of established manufacturers, from HP and Xerox, to Samsung, Canon, Brother, Epson, Kodak, Okidata, Panasonic and more to make sure you find the printer that most closely meets your requirements. In choosing a printer, you need to determine first what your main use will be. If it's text documents, it's one sort; if photos and brochures, something else. Think about the size of the documents you'll be printing -- letter and legal can be handled by almost all of them, but if you need a printer that can handle tabloid or larger jobs, you'll need something more powerful. Specialty photo printers offer a compact alternative if all you're doing is making copies of pix from your digital camera. Consider whether you need a networked or workgroup printer, capable of handling input from a number of computers. The All-in-One printers/scanner/fax machines offer a collection of services in one versatile yet compact machine.", "parent_text": "Printers / Scanners & Supplies", "keyword_density": {"multifunction devices": "0.9", "printers": "2.3"}, "department_id": 1},
{"department_text": "Computer Hardware", "nr_products": 434, "level": -1, "url": "http://www.newegg.com/Fax-Machines-Copiers/SubCategory/ID-351", "text": "Fax Machines & Copiers", "department_url": "http://www.newegg.com/Computer-Hardware/Store", "description_title": "Fax Machines", "parent_url": "http://www.newegg.com/Printers-Scanners-Supplies/Category/ID-33", "keyword_count": {"fax": 8, "fax machines": 5, "machines": 6}, "description_wc": 211, "description_text": "Many fax machines are integrated with telephones, copiers, and computer printers. If you need one of each, purchasing a four-in-one or three-in-one device can save you a considerable amount of money, especially if you purchase your fax machine here at Newegg. We offer state-of-the-art technology at the best prices you will find at any store. Features and Applications of Our Fax Machines Scanning and printing capabilities are two of the most important aspects of any fax machine, photo copier, or printer. If you prefer to have the capability to send and receive color documents, there are plenty of color fax machines in our online catalog. Surprisingly, color fax machines are not much more expensive than black-and-white-only machines. Modem speed is probably the most important thing you will look for in a fax machine. The slower the speed the lower the amount of pages you can transmit in a minute. Most fax machines today are in the 14.4Kbps or 33.6Kbs ranges and perform quite quick with transmission speeds between 6 seconds (slower models) and 2 seconds (faster models) per page. Manufacturers that we carry include Brother, Xerox, Hewlett-Packard, and Canon all with print options of color inkjet, thermal inkjet, or laser.", "parent_text": "Printers / Scanners & Supplies", "keyword_density": {"fax": "3.8", "fax machines": "4.7", "machines": "2.8"}, "department_id": 1},
{"department_text": "Computer Hardware", "nr_products": 1738, "level": -1, "url": "http://www.newegg.com/Barcode-Scanners/SubCategory/ID-583", "text": "Barcode Scanners", "department_url": "http://www.newegg.com/Computer-Hardware/Store", "description_title": "Barcode Scanners", "parent_url": "http://www.newegg.com/Printers-Scanners-Supplies/Category/ID-33", "keyword_count": {"barcode scanners": 4, "barcode": 6, "scanners": 5}, "description_wc": 289, "description_text": "The point of sale (POS) terminal is one of the most important locations in every business, whether it's a multinational chain or a local convenience store. It's inefficient for employees to manually enter every Universal Product Code (UPC). If customers have large purchase orders, it may take awhile for those transactions to be completed. Barcode scanners can simplify the entire process and save time during checkouts. These devices read barcodes and enter the product information directly to your registers. Employees simply wave the readers over items to check the prices. Every POS terminal is different and there are various scanner models for every system. USB barcode scanners can be used with almost every register. As long you have an available USB port you can sync the reader to your system and start ringing items. Employees shouldn't struggle with their hardware. Small problems can cause delays that frustrate customers who are tired of waiting. If a scanner's cord is tangled, associates have to stop helping patrons and untie the knots. Wireless barcode scanners are easy to use and don't require any additional steps to sync with POS terminals. Scanners have many advantages over entering prices or UPCs for every purchase. For example, if your employees manually enter item totals, there's no way to track inventory. Barcode scanners can help connect your registers to your stockroom so you can monitor which products are selling quickly and should be restocked soon. Barcode readers also help employees complete more transactions. Associates only need to press a button to scan an item through. Additionally, workers can interact with patrons and deliver stronger customer service because staffers don't have to read long codes and type them repeatedly.", "parent_text": "Printers / Scanners & Supplies", "keyword_density": {"barcode scanners": "2.8", "barcode": "2.1", "scanners": "1.7"}, "department_id": 1},
