{"department_text": "Computer Hardware", "nr_products": 176, "level": -1, "url": "http://www.newegg.com/Server-Motherboards/SubCategory/ID-302", "text": "Server Motherboards", "department_url": "http://www.newegg.com/Computer-Hardware/Store", "description_title": "Server Motherboards", "parent_url": "http://www.newegg.com/Motherboards/Category/ID-20", "keyword_count": {"motherboards": 5, "server motherboards": 1, "server": 2}, "description_wc": 202, "description_text": "Use this link for more on Server Motherboards in our Learning Center The motherboard, sometimes called the system board or mainboard, is the backbone of the computer and a crucial piece of hardware to which all system components, including the CPU, memory and expansion cards are connected and interact through. Based on the functions of the system, there are various types of motherboards made for different applications. Motherboards for server systems are different from those for home and office use and are enhanced for heavy work and processing loads. With motherboards from manufacturers such as TYAN, Supermicro, ASUS, Intel, Gigabyte and MSI Newegg has a solution for your every need. Select from LGA 775, Dual 771, Dual 1207 and other popular cpu socket types along with various Intel and NVIDIA North Bridges and multiple Front Side Busses. No matter the configuration you are looking for Newegg has the right motherboard for you and at a price you'll like. WARNING: Products with exposed solder may contain lead, a chemical known to the State of California to cause cancer, birth defects and other reproductive harm. Please wash hands after handling internal components and motherboards and avoid inhalation of fumes if heating the solder.", "parent_text": "Motherboards", "keyword_density": {"server motherboards": "1.0", "motherboards": "2.5", "server": "1.0"}, "department_id": 1},
