{"department_text": "Computer Hardware", "nr_products": 38, "level": -1, "url": "http://www.newegg.com/Embedded-Solutions/SubCategory/ID-446", "text": "Embedded Solutions", "department_url": "http://www.newegg.com/Computer-Hardware/Store", "description_title": "Embedded Solution", "parent_url": "http://www.newegg.com/Motherboards/Category/ID-20", "keyword_count": {"embedded": 6, "embedded solution": 4}, "description_wc": 232, "description_text": "Embedded Solution provides PC builders ample flexibility to assemble affordable cost and feature-rich systems, and drive energy conservation into system without compromising performance, compatibility, graphics performance and other features. We offer a wide range of versatile, quality embedded solution for easy deployment to build NVR/DVT, storage devices, digital signage, POS system, Home Theater PC and Thin Client PC for your home or commercial use. Comparing with the conventional motherboard, Embedded Solution provides better time & space-saving for Do-It-Yourself users and deliver faster time-to-market demands for commercial segment. Understanding Motherboard Specifications Motherboard (alternatively known as mainboard, system board or logic board), the \u2018mother\u2019 of all components, is the main printed circuit board found in personal computers, workstations and other computing system. Its embedded chipset holds a key function to connect many of the crucial pc components of the system, such as CPU, Memory, Hard Drive, Graphics Card and other I/O cards. And also, it provides the connectivity for other external peripherals thru I/O connectors, like keyboard and mouse. Each embedded processor and chipset have their own unique design determining system performance, power efficiency, thermal dispersion, upgradability and connectivity. Form factor is another crucial element to consider for expandability. It\u2019s important to acknowledge embedded solution is specifically designed for different applications. Use this link for more information on Motherboard Installation in our Learning Center", "parent_text": "Motherboards", "keyword_density": {"embedded solution": "3.5", "embedded": "2.6"}, "department_id": 1},
