{"department_text": "Computer Hardware", "nr_products": 9, "level": -1, "url": "http://www.newegg.com/CPU-Accessories/SubCategory/ID-151", "text": "CPU Accessories", "department_url": "http://www.newegg.com/Computer-Hardware/Store", "description_title": "CPU Accessories", "parent_url": "http://www.newegg.com/CPUs-Processors/Category/ID-34", "keyword_count": {"accessories": 5, "cpu": 6, "cpu accessories": 4}, "description_wc": 252, "description_text": "You can get all the CPU accessories you need at Newegg. We sell thousands of products from hundreds of networking experts, including everything you need to maintain networking productivity. Hiccups are inevitable. Finding an affordable solution could mean the difference between fluid networking and interrupted workflow. In addition to an all-inclusive inventory of hardware, a wide selection of add-on accessories makes shopping at Newegg even easier. Inexpensive CPU Accessories Searching for a fan connector adapter? Without the right flow of air around your hardware, you could be risking performance and putting your data in jeopardy. You can find a generic connector (3-pin to 4-pin) for just a few dollars. Isn't maintaining the integrity of your information worth a few bucks? AMD backing plates are used in conjunction with a heatsink. These small yet extremely important CPU accessories are essential for smooth networking operations. Created by Swiftech, these plates are available in both bronze and chrome. Is your cooling fan not getting the job done? Perhaps you need a Coolmax sensitive fan adapter? Or better yet, a Thermaltake CPU ducting fan? These components will help increase airflow while minimizing the sound coming from your CPU. Newegg is the one-stop source for your CPU accessories. WARNING: Products with exposed solder may contain lead, a chemical known to the State of California to cause cancer, birth defects and other reproductive harm. Please wash hands after handling internal components and motherboards and avoid inhalation of fumes if heating the solder.", "parent_text": "CPUs / Processors", "keyword_density": {"cpu accessories": "3.2", "accessories": "2.0", "cpu": "2.4"}, "department_id": 1},
