{"department_text": "Computer Hardware", "nr_products": 99, "level": -1, "url": "http://www.newegg.com/Processors-Servers/SubCategory/ID-727", "text": "Processors - Servers", "department_url": "http://www.newegg.com/Computer-Hardware/Store", "description_title": "Intel and AMD CPUs / Processors", "parent_url": "http://www.newegg.com/CPUs-Processors/Category/ID-34", "keyword_count": {"intel and amd": 1, "processors": 3, "cpus processors": 1}, "description_wc": 179, "description_text": "Use this link for more on CPUs / Processors in our Learning Center One of the most exciting components in the computer is the CPU (Central Processing Unit), which is essentially the brain of the computer. It interprets and executes instructions and data contained in software programs as well as the commands of its user. The more generic term 'processor' is often used to refer to a CPU as well. The power and performance of the CPU are the greatest determinants of a computer's overall performance. The CPU battlefield is dominated by two companies, Intel and AMD and their processors are forever pushing the performance of each other. Regardless of whether you are looking to place the CPU in a server, desktop, laptop or other mobile device Newegg has the right solution for you. We carry processors for multiple socket types and series ranging from Pentium's, Athlon's, Celeron's, Core 2's, Core Duo's, Dual Core, Quad Core, Xeon, Opteron, Phenom Sempron, Turion and more. For all your CPU / Processor needs Newegg has you covered.", "parent_text": "CPUs / Processors", "keyword_density": {"intel and amd": "1.7", "processors": "1.7", "cpus processors": "1.1"}, "department_id": 1},
{"department_text": "Computer Hardware", "nr_products": 4, "level": -1, "url": "http://www.newegg.com/Processors-Mobile/SubCategory/ID-759", "text": "Processors - Mobile", "department_url": "http://www.newegg.com/Computer-Hardware/Store", "description_title": "Intel and AMD CPUs / Processors", "parent_url": "http://www.newegg.com/CPUs-Processors/Category/ID-34", "keyword_count": {"intel and amd": 1, "cpus": 7, "processors": 6, "amd": 5, "intel": 6, "cpus processors": 3}, "description_wc": 230, "description_text": "Use this link for more on CPUs / Processors in our Learning Center The most critical component in any computer is the CPU (Central Processing Unit), where all of the \"computing\" actually occurs. It interprets and executes instructions and data contained in software programs, incoming signals from network sources, and the commands of its user. The more generic term 'processor' is often used to refer to a CPU, as well. The power and performance of the CPU are the prime determinants of a computer's overall performance. Mobile CPUs also be called mobile processors, laptop CPUs or laptop processors. Mobile CPUs are designed to save power on portable computers. Mobile CPUs/Processors use lower voltages than desktop processors and have more \"sleep mode\" capability. Mobile CPUs/Processors can be throttled down to different power levels and/or sections of the chip can be turned off entirely when not in use. The two largest CPU / Processor manufacturers are Intel and AMD. Newegg offers the most popular mobile or laptop CPUs with the best prices. Intel Core 2 Duo T7500, Intel Core 2 Duo T9600, Intel Core 2 Duo T7700, Intel Core 2 Duo T9400, Intel Core 2 Duo T8300 are among our constant inventory. AMD Turion 64 MT32, AMD Turion 64 X2 TL-52, AMD Turion 64 MT34, and AMD Turion 64 X2 TL-56 round out the array Newegg carries.", "parent_text": "CPUs / Processors", "keyword_density": {"intel and amd": "1.3", "intel": "2.6", "processors": "2.6", "cpus": "3.1", "amd": "2.2", "cpus processors": "2.6"}, "department_id": 1},
{"department_text": "Computer Hardware", "level": 0, "url": "http://www.newegg.com/CD-DVD-Blu-Ray-Burners-Media/Category/ID-10", "text": "CD / DVD / Blu-Ray Burners & Media", "department_url": "http://www.newegg.com/Computer-Hardware/Store", "description_title": "CD / DVD Burners & Media", "parent_url": "http://www.newegg.com/Computer-Hardware/Store", "keyword_count": {"dvd": 16, "burners": 5, "cd dvd": 6, "cd dvd burners media": 1, "cd": 7, "cd dvd burners": 2, "media": 3, "dvd burners": 3}, "description_wc": 277, "description_text": "Newegg is proud to carry a wide variety of CD / DVD Burners & Media, including Blu-Ray Burners, Blu-Ray Drives, CD / DVD Accessories, CD / DVD Burners, CD / DVD Drives, CD / DVD Media, Duplicators, and External CD / DVD Drives. Blu-Ray Discs are an optical disc storage medium. The physical dimensions of Blu-Ray Discs are the same as DVDs and CDs. The capacity of a Blu-Ray Disc is almost six times of a normal DVD Disc. A single layer Blu-Ray Disc can store 25GB, and the two-layer / double layer Blu-Ray Disc can store 50GB. \"Blu-Ray burners\" refers to two optical disc formats that can be burned, or recorded on. BD-R discs can be written to once and BD-RE can be erased and re-recorded multiple times. The recording speed of BD-R is 4X/6X/8X, BD-RE is 2X. DVDs (also know as Digital Versatile Disc or Digital Video Disc format) are a popular optical disc storage medium. DVD discs can be divided into three categories: single-sided single-layer disc (4.7GB), single-sided double-layer disc (8.0GB) and double-sided double-layer disc (17GB). DVD burners are used to record video onto blank writeable DVD media. The recording speeds of DVD-R and DVD+R are 18X/20X/22X, DVD+R DL is 8X/10X/12X/16X and DVD-RAM is 12X/14X. WARNING: Products with exposed solder may contain lead, a chemical known to the State of California to cause cancer, birth defects and other reproductive harm. Please wash hands after handling internal components and motherboards and avoid inhalation of fumes if heating the solder.", "parent_text": "Computer Hardware", "keyword_density": {"dvd": "5.8", "burners": "1.8", "cd dvd": "4.4", "cd dvd burners media": "1.5", "cd": "2.5", "cd dvd burners": "2.2", "media": "1.1", "dvd burners": "2.2"}, "department_id": 1},
