{"department_text": "Computer Hardware", "nr_products": 354, "level": -1, "url": "http://www.newegg.com/Power-Strips/SubCategory/ID-350", "text": "Power Strips", "department_url": "http://www.newegg.com/Computer-Hardware/Store", "description_title": "Power Strips", "parent_url": "http://www.newegg.com/Computer-Accessories/Category/ID-1", "keyword_count": {"strips": 4, "power strips": 3, "power": 8}, "description_wc": 312, "description_text": "Everything runs on electricity these days, it seems. Even wireless devices need to recharge from time to time, and only solar-powered technology can run without being anchored occasionally to a power source. With so many devices demanding electrical attention, there just aren't enough outlets in any given home to accommodate all of them. That's why power strips are so essential. Any computer, home entertainment system or kitchen appliance will need one or more sockets for each device incorporated in a suite of tools. Some may need a half dozen or more just to achieve basic functionality. Power strips take a single wall outlet and turn it into a hub for devices, providing 2 or 3 extra sockets for extension cord models, or upwards of 10 to 12 for high-traffic areas. Some of these are also outfitted with surge protectors and backup power alerts. These strips will automatically switch off if they detect a jump in electrical current, protecting all devices attached to it. Others will also supply a small amount of energy for a short period and issue an audible chime to alert people nearby that an event has occurred and power needs to be restored. Other safety features also include protective caps to prevent accidental electrocution from an exposed socket, which is great for households with pets or small children. These tools can also help save on your electricity bill. Instead of struggling to manually unplug and reconnect each device when you aren't using it, you can simply flip the power switch on the strip and turn everything off or back on again at once. Power strips are safe, versatile and provide necessary electricity to all the utilities in your home. Be it for recreation or practical use, they are a reliable way of multiplying the number of things you can do in any given room.", "parent_text": "Computer Accessories", "keyword_density": {"strips": "1.3", "power strips": "1.9", "power": "2.6"}, "department_id": 1},
